Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:42.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Ally, can we get a recap?\N{\rCHT}埃莉 能再說一次嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.53,0:00:45.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You remember the Kowolskis? They've owned this shop for 30 years\N{\rCHT}還記得科洛斯基家族嗎? 他們那店已經開了30年了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:49.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,and they are attempting to set a record by making Buffalo's largest cookie.\N{\rCHT}他們想打破水牛鎮最大的曲奇的紀錄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:52.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- and you have to wear this. - A hairnet?\N{\rCHT}- 你一定要戴上這東西 - 這發罩?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.16,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,H.ealth Department.\N{\rCHT}為了公共衛生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:53.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You are kidding.\N{\rCHT}不要說笑了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:56.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If you're around the cookie, you have to have it on.\N{\rCHT}你想要接近那曲奇你就得遵守規矩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:57.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I just did the hair.\N{\rCHT}我才做了這髮型{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:00:58.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The hair is perfect.\N{\rCHT}多好看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.07,0:01:01.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, give it to me.\N{\rCHT}好了好了 給我吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:06.87,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,God... why do you hate me?\N{\rCHT}上帝 你就這麼恨我嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:09.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We're rolling. And speed.\N{\rCHT}開始... 說話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,For three decades, the Kowolski Bakery\N{\rCHT}三十年以來 科洛斯基自助餐廳{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:15.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,has been a mainstay in downtown Buffalo,\N{\rCHT}一直都是水牛鎮中心的神話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:19.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,known for their sinfully sweet, cream-filled Polski pierogies\N{\rCHT}他們以香甜美味的波蘭式曲奇聞名{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.46,0:01:23.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,and the occasional sugar - induced coma that follows.\N{\rCHT}他們的餅令人再三回味{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:26.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Today, in honor of their 30th anniversary,\N{\rCHT}今天 在他們的三十年店慶典禮上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:30.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,they've invited us to ride along as they go for the record\N{\rCHT}他們邀請我們一同見證 他們將打破{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:33.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,on Buffalo's biggest cookie.\N{\rCHT}水牛鎮最大的曲奇的紀錄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.06,0:01:39.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Vol. Do you need a tissue or something?\N{\rCHT}沃爾 要紙巾嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:42.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Can we get Vol a tissue? Or a spoon?\N{\rCHT}你要張紙巾嗎? 還是要個勺子?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:44.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Good thing we're wearing these.\N{\rCHT}我也戴上了這個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:48.16,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I wouldn't want any stray hairs to fall into the booger.\N{\rCHT}以免我的頭髮掉在這破玩意上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:51.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- We doing this again? - No. We can cut to B roll.\N{\rCHT}- 這段會放出去嗎? - 不 我們會剪掉它{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:52.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Moving on!\N{\rCHT}我們繼續{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:56.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Tell me, Mama, why make Buffalo's biggest cookie?\N{\rCHT}老媽媽 告訴我 為什麼你要做最大的曲奇餅?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:02:00.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, man from Health Department say\N{\rCHT}這樣的 衛生局的人來說 說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:04.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,he find rat pellet in our pastry.\N{\rCHT}他們在我的奶油裡發現死老鼠{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:08.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But I say no, is big chocolate sprinkle.\N{\rCHT}我說 那不是 那是一大塊巧克力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:11.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But he shut store down.\N{\rCHT}但他還是封了鋪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:14.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,So we clean up,\N{\rCHT}那我們就搞乾淨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:18.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,make big cookie for to bring customers back.\N{\rCHT}做一個大的曲奇餅 把客人攬回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:22.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, I admire your candor.\N{\rCHT}嗯 你還真坦白{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:23.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's try that again, shall we?\N{\rCHT}我們要重新來一遍嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:28.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Tell me, Mama, why make Buffalo's biggest cookie?\N{\rCHT}老媽媽 告訴我 為什麼要做水牛鎮最大的曲奇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:33.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,So the children of the neighborhood will be happy.\N{\rCHT}這個大麯奇餅一定會令鄰居的小孩很開心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:37.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It must be wonderful seeing the smiles on their little faces.\N{\rCHT}對 能看到他們的小臉上掛著微笑是多麼美好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I work in back. I see no smiles.\N{\rCHT}我在廚房做事 看不到那些微笑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:48.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The previous record was 8 feet 7 inches, baked by Gladys Pelsnick.\N{\rCHT}現在的紀錄是2.60米直徑 是克拉麗斯所創造的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:51.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If this cookie beats that, it will prove\N{\rCHT}如果這塊曲奇能比克拉麗斯的大 那就能證明{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,the Kowolskis have much more free time.\N{\rCHT}科洛斯基家族更加閑著無聊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:57.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And the cookie is... 10 feet, 4 inches!\N{\rCHT}這曲奇是... 3.14米!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:03:00.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We have a new record!\N{\rCHT}新紀錄誕生了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:03.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Cue the cheesy inspirational music!\N{\rCHT}來段破紀錄的音樂!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:24.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But what are we really looking at here?\N{\rCHT}但是在這裡你所發現的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:26.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Is it just a big cookie?\N{\rCHT}只是一個大麯奇嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:29.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Or does this cookie represent the pride of Buffalo?\N{\rCHT}還是一個水牛鎮的驕傲的象徵?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Its hard - working citizens the key ingredient\N{\rCHT}以市民的勤勞和忘我工作作為主材料{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:34.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,with a few nuts thrown in.\N{\rCHT}加上兩塊"傻瓜"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:38.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And finally, the love of our families,\N{\rCHT}最後 再加上家庭的愛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:40.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,which provides the warm center,\N{\rCHT}溫暖的親情{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:45.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,making our beloved Buffalo the sweetest place to live.\N{\rCHT}令我們所愛的水牛鎮成為一個宜人居住的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:48.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And that's the way the cookie crumbles.\N{\rCHT}曲奇是這樣製成的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:51.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm Bruce Nolan, Eyewitness News.\N{\rCHT}這裡是布魯斯·諾蘭 直擊新聞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:54.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And cut.\N{\rCHT}卡...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,So what do you think?\N{\rCHT}覺得怎樣?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:58.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's really good.\N{\rCHT}我覺得很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It sucks. It's a story about a cookie.\N{\rCHT}討厭極了 一個曲奇的故事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:05.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The Pillsbury Doughboy would be riveted.\N{\rCHT}我看起來像個傻子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:09.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It made me laugh. Nothing wrong with making people laugh.\N{\rCHT}親愛的 這很有趣 我都忍不住笑了 讓人笑不好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll never be an anchorman.\N{\rCHT}但這樣我永遠不能成為電視臺的主持{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:13.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The job's there, but I can't reach it.\N{\rCHT}伸手可觸 但我就是得不到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:18.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Every time they make me do this kind of stuff I have to act like a goof.\N{\rCHT}因為我老是在幹這種事情 我要扮得像個傻瓜一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:22.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I have no credibility. Not good.\N{\rCHT}人們覺得我不可靠 這一點也不好... 不好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:24.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Now you just sound silly. - Forget it.\N{\rCHT}- 知道嗎? 你說這話才像個傻瓜 - 算了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:28.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's not important. Let's watch it one more time.\N{\rCHT}這不重要 對嗎? 這不重要 我們再看一遍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:30.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- No. - Once more? Please?\N{\rCHT}- 噢 不 - 就一次 求你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:33.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No! You promised to help me with this photo album.\N{\rCHT}不要 布魯斯 你答應過我會幫我整理照片的!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Now get your gooy butt over here.\N{\rCHT}把你那傻瓜的屁股擺這裡來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:44.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Looking.\N{\rCHT}不要"嗯"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:45.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Ok\N{\rCHT}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:49.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Just go through this stack and pick your favorites.\N{\rCHT}看看這一疊 把你最喜歡的挑出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:56.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on. This is fun, right?\N{\rCHT}看這有趣 不是嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:58.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Isn't this fun? This is nice.\N{\rCHT}真有趣 這張不錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:01.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Evan's going to get that anchor job.\N{\rCHT}如果我能夠成為主持人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Bruce! - He's the favorite.\N{\rCHT}- 布魯斯! - 這才是我最喜歡的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:07.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You know what? Just forget it. This is just our life.\N{\rCHT}算了 算了 這就是我們的生活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We can always just have some kid do it for us.\N{\rCHT}或許生個小孩來整理吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hold the phone.\N{\rCHT}噢 別掛線{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I like this one. Our weekend at the lake.\N{\rCHT}我喜歡這張 我們在湖邊的週末{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:19.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's supposed to be in our private stash.\N{\rCHT}這是我的私人珍藏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:22.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You look perky. Must have been cold. - Give it to me.\N{\rCHT}- 沒有穿衣服啊 一定很冷吧 - 還給我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:25.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I think I'll put this on my computer.\N{\rCHT}我要把它掃描進電腦裡當壁紙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:27.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Give it to me. Come on. - No!\N{\rCHT}- 好了 還給我! - 不不不{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Fine. Do with it what you will.\N{\rCHT}好了 你想幹什麼隨便{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't care.\N{\rCHT}我不理了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I will do with it what I will. - Jesus.\N{\rCHT}- 我會的 - 上帝啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:38.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I might even send this in to Playboy.\N{\rCHT}我會把它送到"花花公子"去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:42.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Their layouts can be quite tasteful. - Give that to me right now!\N{\rCHT}- 聽說他們也刊登讀者來照 - 馬上還給我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:45.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Rough stuff. - I'm going to hurt you.\N{\rCHT}- 專業打手! - 抓住我!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:53.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sweetie? Time to get up.\N{\rCHT}親愛的 要起床了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:58.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Good dream. No.\N{\rCHT}不要 我還在做夢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:12.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The Buffalo Sabres lost again last night to the Toronto Maple Leafs.\N{\rCHT}水牛鎮剃刀隊昨晚又輸一場 他們對陣多倫多楓葉隊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:14.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Of course they did. They're my team.\N{\rCHT}是我支持的球隊 當然輸了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:17.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's the way the cookie crumbles.\N{\rCHT}曲奇是這樣製成的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:20.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There might be something to this cookie line.\N{\rCHT}我想這句曲奇對白不錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:26.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The greatest anchors have a signature sign - off. Like Walter Cronkite.\N{\rCHT}每個台柱都有自己的口頭禪 像沃爾特·克朗凱特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:30.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And that's the way it was.\N{\rCHT}鋼鐵是這樣煉成的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:33.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's the way the cookie crumbles.\N{\rCHT}曲奇是這樣煉成的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:38.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's the way I like it\N{\rCHT}這個就是 啊哈 我喜歡這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:41.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, no.\N{\rCHT}噢 慘了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:43.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Grace, the dog! - I'm in the shower!\N{\rCHT}- 格雷斯 你的狗! - 我在洗澡!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No, Sam. Bad dog.\N{\rCHT}壞狗狗!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Inside, bad. Outside, good.\N{\rCHT}裡面不行 外面行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:02.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You're done now. Great.\N{\rCHT}已經拉完了? 好極了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:05.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,B-E-A-utiful.\N{\rCHT}潑... 伊... 傲... 漂亮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:10.52,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on. Let's go back in and have a shit.\N{\rCHT}來 我們進去拉屎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:19.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What is the dillio? - We are having a blood drive.\N{\rCHT}- 那是在幹什麼? - 在搞獻血活動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:22.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Needles. Yuck. - They need my blood.\N{\rCHT}- 拿針紮人 - 他們需要我的血{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:26.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I have a very rare blood type. I'm AB positive.\N{\rCHT}我的是小血型 AB+型{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:28.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Really? I'm IB positive.\N{\rCHT}是嗎? 我的是IB+型{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:32.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I B positive they ain't touching me with no needle. It's just so...\N{\rCHT}他們不敢拿針動我 這真是... 有意義{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:35.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Helpful and life - saving? - No. It's blood.\N{\rCHT}- 可以救人一命 - 不 這些是血{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:39.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Blood is supposed to stay inside the body, where it's meant to be.\N{\rCHT}血是應該在體內流動的 這才能叫血{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:43.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Besides, they stockpile this stuff in a warehouse, it's all on ice,\N{\rCHT}但這些人 他們把血裝起來再放到什麼室裡倒掉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:45.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,and they say there's a shortage.\N{\rCHT}然後他們就說缺血{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:47.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Where did you hear that?\N{\rCHT}不是這樣的 你哪裡聽回來的?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:49.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,From a friend of a friend\N{\rCHT}從一個政府高官的姨媽的弟弟的侄女{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:52.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,of a girl whose sister is going out with someone in the government.\N{\rCHT}的同學的同事的女友的朋友那裡聽回來的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:55.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,For your protection, I cannot discuss it.\N{\rCHT}但我今天不能跟你討論這問題了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Now get out, before they see us together.\N{\rCHT}出去吧 趁他們還沒見到我們在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:04.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Here. You need these more than I do.\N{\rCHT}等等 你比我更需要這個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:06.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What is "these"?\N{\rCHT}這個是什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:08.66,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Prayer beads. The kids made them for me.\N{\rCHT}護身符 一個小孩做給我的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:12.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- They will keep you safe. - I hope they're powerful.\N{\rCHT}- 能保你平安 - 最好它真能帶來奇跡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:16.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm going to need a friggin' miracle to get to work on time.\N{\rCHT}否則我趕不及上班了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:30.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This isn't happening. Not now. Not during sweeps week.\N{\rCHT}不是吧 別這樣對我 別在這種時候 別在這種時候這樣對我!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, God.\N{\rCHT}上帝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:40.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yup, meeting started without me.\N{\rCHT}好了 開會了 我趕不上了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:42.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is my luck.\N{\rCHT}這就是我的命!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:51.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on.\N{\rCHT}快! 快! 快!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:57.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Jesus.\N{\rCHT}上帝啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Get out of there!\N{\rCHT}出來!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:07.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"Are you blind? " No, but I'm late.\N{\rCHT}你是"瞎子"嗎? 不 但我要遲到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:12.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Is your child in dire jeopardy?\N{\rCHT}你的孩子正面臨死亡的威迫嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:14.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Find out tonight after the game.\N{\rCHT}今晚比賽後告你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:16.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Promos are approved.\N{\rCHT}Ok 通過了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:19.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Jack? Shouldn't we be focusing on Pete's retirement?\N{\rCHT}傑克 我們不是應該關注多點皮特的退休嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:23.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- This is his last week. - Any word on the anchor position?\N{\rCHT}- 這星期以後他就不做了 - 對 他的職位會空出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:26.20,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Evan, when I know something, you'll know something.\N{\rCHT}埃文 我想到的事 你總能想到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:28.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sorry I'm late.\N{\rCHT}對不起 我來遲了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:31.16,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Traffic was...\N{\rCHT}大塞車{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:33.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Did you already play the spots?\N{\rCHT}你們看過我的報導了嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Nice story, but we're going with Evan's piece.\N{\rCHT}你的故事挺有趣 布魯斯 但我們還是挑了埃文的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:39.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The sex scandal in the mayor's office for sweeps.\N{\rCHT}市長內閣的性醜聞事件{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:43.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah. Sweeps.\N{\rCHT}噢 對 醜聞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:46.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And that's the way the cookie crumbles.\N{\rCHT}曲奇是這樣製成的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:50.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm just messing with you, Bruce.\N{\rCHT}我印象深刻 布魯斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:53.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,See, you just gotta remember that the newsroom\N{\rCHT}你要記住 新聞就像{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:56.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,is like a big cookie.\N{\rCHT}一大塊 曲奇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:02.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you like jazz, Evan? Let me play something for you.\N{\rCHT}埃文你喜歡爵士樂嗎? 讓我為你奏一曲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:12.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I can hold that note all day. - Knock it off, guys.\N{\rCHT}- 我可以給你看一整天 - 夥計們 冷靜點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:15.00,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We'll keep your story in reserve.\N{\rCHT}布魯斯 你的報導我會留著後備{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:19.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Can we get back to the board so we'll have something to put on the air today?\N{\rCHT}現在看著白板 看看今天應該播放什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:23.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Great choice, Jack. The Cadillac of bolognas.\N{\rCHT}有眼光 傑克! 這些是最上等的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:25.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Jack, can I talk to you?\N{\rCHT}傑克 能談幾句嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:27.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Sure. What do you need? - Sweeps.\N{\rCHT}- 當然 布魯斯 說吧 - 是報導{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:31.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Jack, hear me out. I'm starting to get desperate.\N{\rCHT}傑克 你一定要幫幫我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:34.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm pushing 40 and what have I got to show?\N{\rCHT}我已經40了 我以後怎麼過?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:36.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I've hit a kind of ceiling.\N{\rCHT}我在這裡已經變了一個傻瓜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:38.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There's an anti - Bruce barrier I can't get past.\N{\rCHT}我的前途有一個"反 布魯斯"的牌子 不讓我通過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:42.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And Evan is loving it.\N{\rCHT}但埃文呢 他受人崇拜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:46.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He gets the stories, he gets on sweeps... I should be more like Evan.\N{\rCHT}他有他的故事 有他的素材 我想我也應該有這樣的待遇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:48.66,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't be like Evan. Evan's an asshole.\N{\rCHT}你想像埃文一樣? 埃文是個混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:51.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I can be an asshole. - No, Bruce. You can't.\N{\rCHT}- 我也可以做個混蛋 - 不 布魯斯 你不能{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:59.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You going to pick that up? - Yeah. I'm sorry.\N{\rCHT}- 還不給我撿起來? - 對不起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:03.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This anchor thing opening up has got me nuts.\N{\rCHT}我太想成為台柱了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:05.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Hi, Susan. - Hi, Jack.\N{\rCHT}- 嗨 蘇珊 - 嗨 傑克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:10.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You're a good reporter. You make people laugh.\N{\rCHT}布魯斯 你是個好記者 你能讓觀眾笑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:14.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,All right. I'll tell you what.\N{\rCHT}好了 這樣吧今天是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:17.77,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Today is the 156th anniversary of the Maid Of The Mist.\N{\rCHT}"霧之少女"號的156歲紀念{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I want you in Niagara Falls in an hour.\N{\rCHT}我要你到瀑布裡呆一個小時 "霧之少女"號製造周年紀念?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:22.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The Maid Of The Mist is always live.\N{\rCHT}那就是直播了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:28.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Evan always does the live feeds. - Now you and Evan get the live feeds.\N{\rCHT}- 但我不是幹直播的人 - 那你現在就是幹直播的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm going live? During sweeps?\N{\rCHT}我要直播新聞?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Watch your step. I've seen your out takes.\N{\rCHT}但小心點布魯斯 這次可不能剪片的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Jack, you will not regret this.\N{\rCHT}傑克 你一定不會後悔的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:38.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And I won't forget you when I go national.\N{\rCHT}我出名後一定不會忘記你的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Can you...?\N{\rCHT}能不能?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:43.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thanks, pal.\N{\rCHT}謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:47.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Can I have your wish now? I'll put it in the wish jar.\N{\rCHT}你的願望星好了嗎? 放到這瓶裡 謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Put your wish in.\N{\rCHT}把願望放到瓶子裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Me, too. - Put your wish in.\N{\rCHT}- 我也有 - 放到這瓶裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.76,0:11:53.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That looks like a big wish.\N{\rCHT}看 這一定是個很大的願望{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:56.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No, Martin, don't eat that.\N{\rCHT}噢 別! 別! 馬克不要吃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:59.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't put that in your mouth. That's paste, honey.\N{\rCHT}這是漿糊 不要放到嘴裡去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:05.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- That must have tasted awful. - Mommy!\N{\rCHT}- 一定是很難吃的 - 媽咪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:10.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Did you have a good time with Aunt Gracie today?\N{\rCHT}今天有沒有聽 格雷斯阿姨的話?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:15.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- See how nice this is? Baby on the hip. - It's amazing. You've become Mom.\N{\rCHT}- 看著多棒 抱著一個寶寶 - 噢 太棒了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:17.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The transformation is complete.\N{\rCHT}你已經是"媽媽"了 成功轉型了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:20.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll get it.\N{\rCHT}我來聽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:22.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Small Wonders Day Care. - Grace?\N{\rCHT}- 小奇觀托兒所 - 格雷斯?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:25.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's Debbie, the sister whose life you're not wasting.\N{\rCHT}不 我是黛比 被你毀掉幸福的人的姐姐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:27.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- OK. - Bye, Debbie!\N{\rCHT}- 好了 我來聽 - 你好 黛比!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hi. Sorry.\N{\rCHT}你好!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:32.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Debbie forgot to take her meds today. Where are you?\N{\rCHT}不要怪黛比 你在哪?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:35.52,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A little place called the winner's circle.\N{\rCHT}一個旅遊勝地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm at the falls, doing a live report.\N{\rCHT}我在瀑布裡 要做現場直播{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:39.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Live? That's great!\N{\rCHT}做現場直播? 那太好了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:43.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah! It's happening, hon. I got sweeps and I'm live.\N{\rCHT}對! 就是這樣 親愛的 像埃文一樣有機會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,They're seeing if I can think on my feet.\N{\rCHT}知道這是什麼意思嗎? 我不用再靠人了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:48.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Like I might have to do in a live anchor situation.\N{\rCHT}我快要成為主持人了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.15,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, my gosh.\N{\rCHT}我的天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:54.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah! Jack practically came out and told me.\N{\rCHT}對!! 實際上 傑克 要讓我上位{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Practically?\N{\rCHT}實際上?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:58.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He didn't spell it out. Legally, he can't.\N{\rCHT}對 他沒有說出來 因為在程式上他不能說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:02.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is what happened to Susan Ortega\N{\rCHT}但現在就像蘇珊·奧爾特加成為真正主持人前{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,before they bumped her up to the desk.\N{\rCHT}所經歷的一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:05.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's good.\N{\rCHT}太好了 太好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:09.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, honey, I just don't want you to get too ahead of yourself.\N{\rCHT}太好了 但親愛的 現在還不應該太高興{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:11.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Bruce. - I got to go!\N{\rCHT}- 布魯斯 - 我要開始了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:14.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- They're calling me in. - OK, honey. Good luck. I love you.\N{\rCHT}- 他們在叫我了 - 好的 親愛的 好運 我愛你!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:18.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's do it.\N{\rCHT}來吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:22.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- They want you close to the falls. - I'm going to get soaked.\N{\rCHT}- 他們向你接近瀑布 - 真的? 那不就要濕了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:25.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's the point. They want you to put this on.\N{\rCHT}正是這樣 他們要你戴上這個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:28.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Part of the condition of us getting the exclusive.\N{\rCHT}保持你一向的形象{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:32.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You know what? Nothing can bother me today. Nothing.\N{\rCHT}知道嗎? 今天我什麼都不介意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:36.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Now remember, it's their 156th - year anniversary.\N{\rCHT}好了記住 是156歲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:40.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,149 capacity. They cater to tourists, honeymooners...\N{\rCHT}有149個旅客 他們有的來度假 有的來度蜜月{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:43.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And people who are insanely thirsty. I get it.\N{\rCHT}還有想來喝水的人 明白了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:46.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You're going to interview Irene Dansfield.\N{\rCHT}還有你要採訪愛琳{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:50.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Irene, a pleasure to meet you. You look beautiful.\N{\rCHT}愛琳! 很高興見到你 真的 你看上去好漂亮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:52.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Irene's mother rode on the maiden voyage.\N{\rCHT}愛琳的母親參加過這船的處女行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:54.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Rub that in my face! - 90 seconds!\N{\rCHT}- 哇! 那可真令人吃驚 - 90秒? 天啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:56.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Holy hell.\N{\rCHT}90秒? 呼...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:00.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Because of the fast response,\N{\rCHT}由於快速行動 所有有毒物質{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:05.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,the chemicals were cleaned up without incident. Susan?\N{\rCHT}在事故發生前已經撤走 蘇珊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:07.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Bruce Nolan is at Niagara Falls.\N{\rCHT}布魯斯·諾蘭 現在正在尼加拉瓜大瀑布前{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:10.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But before we go live to Bruce, we have an announcement.\N{\rCHT}但在布魯斯的直播前 我們有一則重要新聞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:13.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,As everyone knows, after 33 years,\N{\rCHT}大家都知道 我們敬愛的皮特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:16.91,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,our beloved Pete Fineman is retiring.\N{\rCHT}在工作33年後宣佈退休{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:21.66,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Pete's shoes are virtually impossible to fill, but the show must go on.\N{\rCHT}皮特已經不會再工作了 但他的節目還會繼續下去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:27.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And we could think of no one better than our very own Evan Baxter.\N{\rCHT}沒人能代替他的地位 除了埃文·巴克斯特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:30.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, boy!\N{\rCHT}噢 老天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Congratulations. - I'm thrilled and honored.\N{\rCHT}- 恭喜你 埃文 - 謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:38.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,As you said, no one can replace Pete, but I will do my best.\N{\rCHT}像你所說的 沒人能代替偉大的皮特 但我會盡力的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:43.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I am so proud to be a part of our local community of Buffalo.\N{\rCHT}我必須說 能成為水牛鎮的市民很榮幸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:48.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I think, in a lot of ways, a great city is like a great recipe, really.\N{\rCHT}而我相信 一個偉大的城市就像一張偉大的菜譜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:52.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You take hard - working citizens, add some care - givers,\N{\rCHT}放點勤勞 加點團結{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,maybe a few nuts!\N{\rCHT}或許加幾片"傻瓜"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:15:01.16,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,All sprinkled with the love and support of our good families.\N{\rCHT}所有這些再加上來自家庭的愛與鼓勵{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:05.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Ultimately, that makes one sweet place to live.\N{\rCHT}就炒成一道 甜蜜之家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- That was amazing. - I wish I'd written something.\N{\rCHT}- 說的很好 - 沒什麼 只是有感而發{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:10.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And now let's go live to that wacky\N{\rCHT}現在讓我們回到報導現場{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:12.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Bruce Nolan at Niagara Falls.\N{\rCHT}怪人布魯斯·諾蘭 在尼加拉瓜大瀑布報導{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey, wacky Bruce!\N{\rCHT}嘿 怪人 布魯斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:22.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Talk, Bruce. Hello. - Talk, honey.\N{\rCHT}- 布魯斯? 說話啊 布魯斯 喂? - 說話啊 親愛的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:24.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What's going on? - A Walt Disney.\N{\rCHT}- 怎麼回事? - 那個怪人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:26.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- It's frozen solid. - Check the feed.\N{\rCHT}- 他定格了 可能是沒聲音 - 檢查信號{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:29.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We may be having technical difficulty.\N{\rCHT}我們遇到一點技術問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:31.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- The feed's good, Jack. - Come on.\N{\rCHT}- 信號沒問題 傑克 - 說話啊 布魯斯!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:34.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Talk, Bruce, damn it. - Get ready to pull the plug.\N{\rCHT}- 該死的! - 做好最壞打算{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:37.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on, baby. Say something!\N{\rCHT}親愛的 說話啊 說話啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Bruce, talk.\N{\rCHT}布魯斯 說話!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Hi, Susan. - Thank you, God.\N{\rCHT}- 嗨 蘇珊! - 謝天謝地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.87,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Bruce Nolan here,\N{\rCHT}這裡是布魯斯·諾蘭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:49.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,aboard the Maid Of The Mist in fabulous Niagara Falls, New York.\N{\rCHT}我在"霧之少女"號上 身後是紐約美麗的尼加拉瓜大瀑布{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:54.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,First, let me just add another congratulations to Evan Backstabber.\N{\rCHT}首先 讓我恭喜 埃文·巴克斯特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:56.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Pardon me, Bastard... Baxter.\N{\rCHT}應該是埃文大混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:59.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It is good to see what someone with real talent can do\N{\rCHT}讓我們看看他有沒有能耐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:03.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,when great opportunities are given to them instead of me.\N{\rCHT}應付本來應該給我的好機會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:07.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Anyway, I'm here with Katharine Hepburn's mom.\N{\rCHT}無論如何 我身邊的是凱薩琳的母親{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:12.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Why did you throw the Heart of the Ocean jewel over the railing of the Titanic?\N{\rCHT}告訴我 為什麼你要把海洋之心帶上泰坦尼克號?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Did you feel bad letting Leo DiCaprio drown\N{\rCHT}你把利奧納多留在冰水裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:18.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,while you were safe floating on the door?\N{\rCHT}而自己就趴在大門上是不是很過癮?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:19.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Could you have taken turns?\N{\rCHT}你不想換他上去?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:23.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Or were you too afraid to freeze your big fat ass off?\N{\rCHT}還是你的大胖屁股被凍住了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:26.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I guess that's how life is.\N{\rCHT}這就是命{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:30.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Some people are drenched, freezing on a stupid boat with a stupid hat,\N{\rCHT}有些人在冷得要命的船上等死 還要戴著這種帽子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:34.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,while others are in a news studio, sucking up the glory.\N{\rCHT}而另外一些人就舒舒服服 得呆在錄影廠裡領功{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:36.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, well. No big deal.\N{\rCHT}哦 不錯哦 夥計{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:41.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The owner of the Maid Of The Mist. Let's have a talk with him.\N{\rCHT}那是"霧之少女"號的主人 我們跟他談一談{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:44.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on in here, Bill. No, let's have a talk.\N{\rCHT}來這邊 比爾 別別別 我們來談談{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What are you doing?\N{\rCHT}你在幹什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:49.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You've been running the Maid Of The Mist for 23 years.\N{\rCHT}你已經擁有"霧之少女"號23年了 你說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:52.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Why do you think I didn't get anchor?\N{\rCHT}為什麼我不能成為主持人呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I don't want any problems. - Is it my hair?\N{\rCHT}- 我不知道怎麼回事 - 因為我的髮型不好看嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:58.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Are my teeth not white enough? Or, like the great falls,\N{\rCHT}還是我的牙不夠白? 還是我的命就像{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:17:03.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,is the bedrock of my life eroding beneath me?\N{\rCHT}大瀑布下的石頭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:05.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Eroding!\N{\rCHT}你一生都得被我踩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:08.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Eroding!\N{\rCHT}你一生都得被我踩!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Cut the feed. Go to black. - I'm on it.\N{\rCHT}取消直播{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:18.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm Bruce Nolan, for Eyewitness News. Back to you, fuckers!\N{\rCHT}這裡是布魯斯·諾蘭直擊新聞 交給你們 他媽的!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:21.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Oh, boy. - Oh, my God.\N{\rCHT}我的天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:28.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That is perfect.\N{\rCHT}太棒了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:31.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That is the motivation that I needed!\N{\rCHT}這才是我需要的激勵{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:33.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Right there! Thank you!\N{\rCHT}就這樣! 謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:38.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you, WKBW.\N{\rCHT}謝謝 WKBW!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:42.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Wimpy... Kitty Baby Whiners!\N{\rCHT}軟弱無能的基蒂寶貝悲訴者!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's what that stands for!\N{\rCHT}就是代表這個意思{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:48.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll see you on Channel 5.\N{\rCHT}我要跳去5頻道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:50.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Where they do the real news!\N{\rCHT}他們才是真正報導新聞的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.83,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Do I look blind to you?\N{\rCHT}我看起來很盲目嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:59.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's go, man. Come on.\N{\rCHT}我們走吧 快點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:01.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What are you doing?\N{\rCHT}你們在幹什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:04.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on. Leave the poor guy alone!\N{\rCHT}不要搞這可憐的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:07.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You OK, man?\N{\rCHT}你沒事吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, you better keep walking.\N{\rCHT}你們有種就別走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:14.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What'd you say, ese? - Run, man!\N{\rCHT}- 什麼? 你說什麼? - 快逃阿!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Run!\N{\rCHT}快跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:19.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, God!\N{\rCHT}上帝!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:23.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,OK, I didn't mean it!\N{\rCHT}好了好了 我不是認真的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:27.16,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I was just kidding! - Hey, you forgot your things.\N{\rCHT}- 開玩笑的 - 嘿 你忘記拿東西了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:33.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Say something now!\N{\rCHT}看你還敢多嘴 還敢再說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:40.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,B - E - A...\N{\rCHT}潑... 伊... 傲... 漂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:43.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,..utiful.\N{\rCHT}漂亮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:49.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's what I get...\N{\rCHT}這就是報應{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:53.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's what I get for trying to help someone.\N{\rCHT}我幫人的報應{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:57.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't look at me, Walter.\N{\rCHT}不要望著我 沃爾特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:59.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, no!\N{\rCHT}噢 不!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:06.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's my payment, I guess.\N{\rCHT}我想這就是我的報應了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:08.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That is my reward.\N{\rCHT}我應得的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:16.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Just? Just get a clue!\N{\rCHT}人生就是? 就是尋尋覓覓!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:19.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank God you're all right.\N{\rCHT}感謝上帝 你沒事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:22.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,God, yeah. Let's thank God.\N{\rCHT}上帝... 我們要感謝上帝嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:25.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,For his blessings are raining down upon me.\N{\rCHT}感謝他的祝福降臨在我身上.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:28.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Wait! That's not rain! - Bruce, please don't do that.\N{\rCHT}- 不過 這不是雨嘛? - 別這樣 布魯斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:30.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Everything happens for a reason.\N{\rCHT}凡事看開點...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:34.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That I don't need. That is a clich? That is not helpful.\N{\rCHT}這種陳詞濫調對我沒用 我不需要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:36.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"A bird in the hand is worth two in the bush."\N{\rCHT}"二鳥在林不如一鳥在手"!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I have no bird! No bush! God has taken my bird and my bush.\N{\rCHT}我沒有鳥! 也沒有林!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:43.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I see. So God is picking on you?\N{\rCHT}上帝把我的鳥從我的林裡拿走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:45.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No! He's ignoring me completely.\N{\rCHT}噢... 我明白了... 你是說上帝是故意找你的碴? 是不是?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:49.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He's busy giving Evan everything he wants.\N{\rCHT}他在忙著滿足埃文!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:53.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Great, Sam. But you missed your target. I'm over here!\N{\rCHT}你太棒了 薩姆... 但你搞錯目標了 我在這裡!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:56.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't get mad at the dog. It's not his fault.\N{\rCHT}又不是狗的錯 幹嘛沖他發火!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:59.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's God's fault. He gave him the wrong co - ordinates.\N{\rCHT}對 是上帝的錯 他把一切都搞亂套了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:02.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Enough! Will you stop being such a martyr?\N{\rCHT}夠了 說的好像你被人謀殺了一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I am not being a martyr! I'm a victim!\N{\rCHT}我不是被人謀殺 我是個犧牲品!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:08.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,God is a mean kid with a magnifying glass, and I'm the ant.\N{\rCHT}上帝是個壞小孩 他坐在那裡 手上拿著放大鏡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:10.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He could fix my life if he wanted,\N{\rCHT}他只要5分種就能改變我的命運 如果他高興的話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:14.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,but he'd rather burn off my feelers and watch me squirm.\N{\rCHT}可他卻放任那個傢伙對我為所欲為!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:16.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sweetheart, I know you're mad.\N{\rCHT}我知道你很生氣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:20.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What Evan did was slimy and wrong.\N{\rCHT}我完全明白埃文對你做的一切都是錯的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:24.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This day could have been so much worse. I'm just glad you're OK.\N{\rCHT}但我真的很高興你今天能平安無事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:27.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,OK? News flash! I'm not OK.\N{\rCHT}平安無事? "新聞簡訊"呢? 我有事!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm not OK with a mediocre job!\N{\rCHT}我討厭我做的那些平庸的事情!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:31.20,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Or a mediocre apartment!\N{\rCHT}我討厭我住的這間平庸的公寓!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:33.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm not OK with a mediocre life!\N{\rCHT}我討厭我過的這種平庸的生活!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:45.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Is that what you think we have? A mediocre life?\N{\rCHT}我們在一起 也是平庸的生活?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:47.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't make this about you.\N{\rCHT}別把這件事情扯到你身上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:51.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,About me? How could I make this about me?\N{\rCHT}什麼... 怎麼可能扯到我身上?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:54.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's about you. It's always about you.\N{\rCHT}這是你的事情 永遠都是你的事情{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:57.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Perfect.\N{\rCHT}太好了! 太好了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:59.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll have the worst day of my life with\N{\rCHT}今天是我一生中最糟的一天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:01.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,a side order of guilt, please!\N{\rCHT}請不要再讓我有罪惡感了 行嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:10.91,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,OK, God. You want me to talk to you?\N{\rCHT}好罷... 上帝 你要和我說話嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:14.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Then talk back. Tell me what's going on.\N{\rCHT}那就回答我 告訴我這是怎麼了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:17.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What should I do? Give me a signal.\N{\rCHT}我該怎麼辦? 給我個信號吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:23.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I need your guidance, Lord. Please, send me a sign.\N{\rCHT}你指引過什麼人嗎? 給我指示吧!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:29.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, what's this joker doing now?\N{\rCHT}噢 現在又在耍什麼把戲?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:38.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,OK. All right. I'll try it your way.\N{\rCHT}好... 好吧... 我就試試你的方式{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:44.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,All right. Lord... I need a miracle.\N{\rCHT}好的... 主啊... 我需要奇跡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:47.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm desperate.\N{\rCHT}我很絕望...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.48,0:21:49.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I need your help, Lord.\N{\rCHT}我需要你的説明 主啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:51.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Please, reach into my life...\N{\rCHT}求你了... 進入我的生活...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:57.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What the...? Where are you?\N{\rCHT}你在那兒啊?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:21:59.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Got you!\N{\rCHT}我靠...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.41,0:22:43.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Fine!\N{\rCHT}好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.87,0:22:45.83,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The gloves are off, pal!\N{\rCHT}手鏈已經脫掉了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:48.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on! Let me see a little wrath!\N{\rCHT}來吧 譴責我吧!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:52.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Smite me, O mighty smiter!\N{\rCHT}毀滅我吧! 噢... 你不是很厲害的嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.17,0:22:55.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You're the one who should be fired!\N{\rCHT}你才是該被炒魷魚的人!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:23:00.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The only one around here not doing his job is you!\N{\rCHT}你才是從來不做事的人! 是你!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:03.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Answer me!\N{\rCHT}回答我啊!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.32,0:23:20.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sorry. Don't know you.\N{\rCHT}不好意思... 我不認識你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.41,0:23:23.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Wouldn't call you if I did.\N{\rCHT}認識你的話... 我就會回電話了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.30,0:23:38.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, God!\N{\rCHT}不要 上帝 不要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.93,0:23:47.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hello, 555-0123.\N{\rCHT}你好... 555-0123{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:16.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, no! Sam, this has got to stop!\N{\rCHT}天啊 不要! 停止吧!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.59,0:24:22.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Get it straight. That's the house. This is the bathroom.\N{\rCHT}好了 我們直說吧 那是房子 這是廁所{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.35,0:24:26.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,House, bathroom. Bathroom, house.\N{\rCHT}房子... 廁所... 廁所... 房子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.06,0:24:30.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What's the point?\N{\rCHT}真是對狗彈琴...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.38,0:24:58.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,555-0123...\N{\rCHT}555轉0123...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.72,0:25:03.64,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Denied that promotion? Is life unfair?\N{\rCHT}"升職被拒了嗎? " "生活是不是很不公平? "{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.72,0:25:06.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Is someone less talented than you reaping the benefits?\N{\rCHT}"比你差的人卻搶走了本該屬於你的一切? "{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.06,0:25:08.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Is your name Bruce?\N{\rCHT}"你的名字是布魯斯嗎? "{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.77,0:25:10.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Then do we have the job for you!\N{\rCHT}"那麼我們有份工作要給你"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.02,0:25:14.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We're located at 77256, 23rd Street.\N{\rCHT}"我們在第23大街77256號"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.48,0:25:17.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,So come on down - or we'll just keep beeping you.\N{\rCHT}"快來吧 不然我們會一直呼你的! "{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.04,0:25:36.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"Omni Presents."\N{\rCHT}"全能的現在"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.92,0:25:41.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, yeah. The glass is half - full.\N{\rCHT}... 玻璃半關著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.85,0:25:47.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on! Look! What is that?\N{\rCHT}天啊! 看看吧! 那是什麼! 那是什麼!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.44,0:25:54.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you again.\N{\rCHT}天呐... 謝謝... 再次感謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.82,0:26:04.91,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What the...?\N{\rCHT}這...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.00,0:26:14.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You're looking for room 7.\N{\rCHT}你要去7號房{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.54,0:26:19.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Yeah, I figured. - Want me to even those up for you?\N{\rCHT}- 是的 我想是 - 你這樣沒事嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.47,0:26:27.64,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- How do I get to room 7? - That'd be on the 7th floor.\N{\rCHT}- 7號房怎麼走? - 在7樓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.72,0:26:31.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Stairs are over there. - I'll take the elevator.\N{\rCHT}- 樓梯在那邊 - 好 我坐電梯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.43,0:26:35.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Out of order. - The stairs were my second choice.\N{\rCHT}- 電梯壞了 - 但其實我也蠻喜歡走樓梯的 它是我的第二選擇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.19,0:26:37.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you mind giving me a hand with this floor?\N{\rCHT}你能幫我清潔這一層嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.98,0:26:41.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What? That's good.\N{\rCHT}什麼?... 不錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.99,0:26:43.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you serious?\N{\rCHT}你說真的?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.82,0:26:48.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm kind of busy. Rain check.\N{\rCHT}我有點忙 留著我下次做吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.79,0:26:51.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll hold you to it.\N{\rCHT}等你哦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.25,0:26:54.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm free on the 7th at 7.00.\N{\rCHT}7點我有空 7點!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.25,0:27:00.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The 7th at 7.00 it is.\N{\rCHT}7點就7點吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.38,0:27:05.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This looks promising.\N{\rCHT}他很守信用啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.02,0:27:13.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hello?\N{\rCHT}有人嗎!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.10,0:27:16.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Another hug antic, gnostic waste of my life.\N{\rCHT}這樣浪費我的時間真有創意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.86,0:27:19.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hello?\N{\rCHT}有人嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.78,0:27:23.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm looking for whoever runs this joint!\N{\rCHT}你是這裡的頭頭嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.15,0:27:25.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Be right with you. I'm fixing a light.\N{\rCHT}就來 我在修燈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.95,0:27:28.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Tell me if it's working.\N{\rCHT}幫我看看修好了沒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.20,0:27:30.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah. Seems to be.\N{\rCHT}是的 好象是修好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.45,0:27:34.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Kind of bright, though. - Yeah. It is for most people.\N{\rCHT}- 不過有點刺眼 - 是的 大多數人都是這樣...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.50,0:27:38.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Spend their lives in the dark, trying to hide from me.\N{\rCHT}在黑暗裡度過一生... 想要躲開我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.50,0:27:42.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The elevator's broken, huh?\N{\rCHT}電梯不是壞了嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.76,0:27:45.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, but I'll get around to it.\N{\rCHT}對 不過... 我會修好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.09,0:27:50.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You installed a clapper? - No, but catchy jingle, isn't it?\N{\rCHT}- 你裝了聲控裝置? - 沒有... 不過那首廣告曲很好玩對吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.64,0:27:53.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Clap on, clap off\N{\rCHT}"拍手打開... 拍手關閉... "{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.85,0:27:56.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The clapper\N{\rCHT}啪啪牌聲控{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.52,0:28:00.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Just can't get it out of my head.\N{\rCHT}繞梁三日啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.15,0:28:02.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, good luck with that.\N{\rCHT}那麼祝你好運...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.61,0:28:04.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I'm going to go now. - OK.\N{\rCHT}- 現在我要走了 - 好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.53,0:28:06.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But the boss will be right out.\N{\rCHT}老闆馬上就來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.83,0:28:19.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You must be Bruce. I've been expecting you.\N{\rCHT}你一定是布魯斯 我一直在等你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.42,0:28:23.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is hilarious.\N{\rCHT}有意思...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.34,0:28:26.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You're the boss, electrician and janitor.\N{\rCHT}你是老闆 又是電工 還是清潔工?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.17,0:28:28.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Must be a killer Christmas party.\N{\rCHT}這一定是瘋狂聖誕派對?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.26,0:28:31.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't get drunk, though. One of you might need a ride home.\N{\rCHT}那別喝醉了哦... 要我送你回去嘛?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.10,0:28:36.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You always were funny, Bruce. Just like your father.\N{\rCHT}你總是很會逗人開心 布魯斯 和你父親一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.35,0:28:40.15,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He didn't mind rolling up his sleeves either.\N{\rCHT}他也不介意卷起袖子幹活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.23,0:28:45.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,People underestimate the benefit of manual labor. There's freedom in it.\N{\rCHT}人們常常會低估體力勞動的好處{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.19,0:28:47.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Some of the happiest people smell to\N{\rCHT}那些工作一天后回到家裡 滿身汗臭的人們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.95,0:28:49.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,high heaven at the end of the day.\N{\rCHT}他們才是世界上最幸福的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.45,0:28:52.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, what is this?\N{\rCHT}這是怎麼回事?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.70,0:28:54.20,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How do you know my father\N{\rCHT}我自己都不認識我父親 你是怎麼認識的?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.23,0:28:55.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,and how did you get my number?\N{\rCHT}還有 你是怎麼知道我的呼機號的?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.79,0:28:57.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I know a lot about you, Bruce.\N{\rCHT}我知道你的事情可多了... 布魯斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.08,0:29:01.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Just about everything there is to know.\N{\rCHT}不是每件事情都說得出原因的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.46,0:29:07.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Everything you've ever said or done or thought about doing.\N{\rCHT}你說過的每一句話 做過的每一件事 心中轉過的每一個念頭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.30,0:29:11.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Right there in that file cabinet.\N{\rCHT}都在那個檔櫃裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.72,0:29:15.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Wow! A whole drawer, just for me. - Yeah.\N{\rCHT}- 喔... 我的整櫃人生嗎? - 對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.39,0:29:17.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Mind if I take a look?\N{\rCHT}我可以看一下嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.98,0:29:20.52,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's your life.\N{\rCHT}這是你的生活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.60,0:29:22.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This oughta be good.\N{\rCHT}聽上去不錯...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.99,0:29:39.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This last entry was a little disturbing.\N{\rCHT}最後一筆記錄有點煩人.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.63,0:29:53.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"The gloves are off, God."\N{\rCHT}"手鏈脫掉了 上帝... "{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.76,0:29:56.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"God has taken my bird and my bush."\N{\rCHT}"上帝把我的鳥和我的林都搶走了"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.43,0:29:59.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"God is a mean kid with a magnifying glass."\N{\rCHT}"上帝是個拿著放大鏡的壞小孩"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.93,0:30:03.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"Smite me, O mighty smiter."\N{\rCHT}"毀滅我吧 萬能的毀滅者"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.31,0:30:07.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm not much for blaspheming, but that last one made me laugh.\N{\rCHT}我不怎麼支持褻瀆神靈 不過最後這條記錄讓我捧腹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.48,0:30:09.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you spying on me?\N{\rCHT}你監視我?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.03,0:30:15.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Who are you?\N{\rCHT}你是誰?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.70,0:30:17.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I am the One.\N{\rCHT}我就是那個人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.87,0:30:21.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Creator of the heavens and the earth. Alpha and Omega.\N{\rCHT}我創造了天與地... 以及世間的一切{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.54,0:30:24.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I see where this is going.\N{\rCHT}噢... 我明白這是怎麼回事了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.00,0:30:27.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Bruce... I am God.\N{\rCHT}布魯斯 我是上帝!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.88,0:30:29.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Bingo! Yahtzee!\N{\rCHT}猜中了! 對呀!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.01,0:30:34.14,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Is that your final answer? Our survey says, "God! "\N{\rCHT}這是你的最終答案嗎? 答案是... 上帝!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.85,0:30:37.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It was nice to meet you, God.\N{\rCHT}很高興認識你 上帝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.76,0:30:41.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thanks for the Grand Canyon. Good luck with the Apocalypse.\N{\rCHT}謝謝你創造了大峽谷 希望你世界末日那天平安無事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.48,0:30:44.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And by the way, you suck!\N{\rCHT}順便說一句... 你太失敗了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.02,0:30:47.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It would have been more impressive\N{\rCHT}如果你不用這個蹩腳的櫃子當道具{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.15,0:30:50.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,if you hadn't used the cheesy file cabinet illusion.\N{\rCHT}你的表演會顯得更真實一些{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.32,0:30:53.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Anybody with a brain stem can tell that drawer\N{\rCHT}只要是有腦子的人都看得出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.20,0:30:55.91,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,is being fed through the wall from the other side.\N{\rCHT}這個櫃子是從牆的反面彈出來的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.99,0:30:59.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,All you have to do is find the crease right around here.\N{\rCHT}我只需要找到這條縫...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.12,0:31:02.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There is a seam here, or a hollow spot.\N{\rCHT}就在這裡... 只要找到空心的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.34,0:31:09.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Where?\N{\rCHT}在哪裡?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.34,0:31:11.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Through the dry wall and concrete?\N{\rCHT}隔著牆和磚的那一面嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.47,0:31:17.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,OK, that is a good one.\N{\rCHT}很了不起! 真的很了不起!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.18,0:31:22.64,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- How many fingers am I holding up? - Thou shalt not tempt the Lord.\N{\rCHT}- 好... 猜我伸出了幾隻手指? - 布魯斯 決不要讓上帝...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.73,0:31:24.64,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- If you can't do it... - Three.\N{\rCHT}- 猜不出也沒什麼的... - 3!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.73,0:31:26.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Two... four... nine.\N{\rCHT}二... 四... 九.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.90,0:31:28.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Six... eight... one.\N{\rCHT}六... 八... 一.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.23,0:31:32.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,OK.\N{\rCHT}好...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.49,0:31:35.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How many now?\N{\rCHT}現在呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.45,0:31:36.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Seven.\N{\rCHT}七{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.83,0:31:45.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- How? - You've been complaining about me.\N{\rCHT}- 怎麼會... - 你總是對我抱怨個不停 布魯斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.71,0:31:48.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I'm tired of it. - Don't come near me. Seriously.\N{\rCHT}- 說實話 我快要受不了了 - 等等 別靠近我 說真的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.88,0:31:51.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't want to hurt you,\N{\rCHT}我被逼急了會變成只野獸的 我不想傷害到你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.34,0:31:52.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,but I will out of instinct.\N{\rCHT}但這是我的本能{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.13,0:31:56.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You haven't won a fight since grade 5, and that was against a girl.\N{\rCHT}你最後一次打架是在五年級 和一個女生...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.64,0:32:00.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But she was huge. She'd been held back.\N{\rCHT}但她很壯... 最後退卻的也是她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.51,0:32:02.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And the sun was in your eyes.\N{\rCHT}你眼中的有的是太陽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.77,0:32:04.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Ah, the ego.\N{\rCHT}而不是妄自菲薄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.81,0:32:07.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Anyway, I brought you here to offer you a job.\N{\rCHT}不管怎麼說 讓你來這裡是有工作要給你做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.56,0:32:10.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- A job? What job? - My job.\N{\rCHT}- 工作... 什麼工作? - 我的工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.27,0:32:13.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You think you can do it better, so here's your chance.\N{\rCHT}既然你覺得你可以做得更好 我就給你這個機會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.69,0:32:17.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,When you leave this building, you will be endowed with all my powers.\N{\rCHT}當你離開這座大樓的時候 你會擁有我所有的神力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.78,0:32:20.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sure. Whatever you say, pal.\N{\rCHT}沒問題 隨你怎麼說了 兄台{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.91,0:32:27.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,OK. That did not happen. No one needs to hear about it.\N{\rCHT}好了 什麼都沒發生過 沒有人會知道這個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.87,0:32:29.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm deleting the program.\N{\rCHT}除非我在節目中報導{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.71,0:32:33.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No.\N{\rCHT}不... 不...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.50,0:32:35.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm having a breakdown.\N{\rCHT}這是我的幻覺 我的精神狀況一團糟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.47,0:32:39.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Everyday psychotic episode, caused by a tumor, a brain lesion.\N{\rCHT}這很正常... 心理作用 由腫瘤壓迫大腦產生的幻覺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.01,0:32:42.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on. Start!\N{\rCHT}快... 發動!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.06,0:32:46.14,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That was lucky.\N{\rCHT}碰巧走運而已{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.77,0:32:52.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on. Calm down.\N{\rCHT}拜託... 冷靜下來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.82,0:32:55.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You did not meet God. You do not have his powers.\N{\rCHT}你不是上帝... 你也沒有神力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.49,0:32:58.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If that was God, I'm Clint Eastwood.\N{\rCHT}如果他是上帝 我就是克林特·伊斯特伍德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.95,0:33:01.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Holy hell!\N{\rCHT}天啊!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.75,0:33:09.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Be careful what you wish for, punk.\N{\rCHT}小心別許錯了願哦... 笨蛋!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.21,0:33:11.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Nope!\N{\rCHT}不! 不!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.17,0:33:16.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I am a reasonable, sane human being.\N{\rCHT}我是個理智的人類!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.01,0:33:18.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,With a.44 Magnum.\N{\rCHT}點44左輪...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.93,0:33:21.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The most powerful handgun in the...\N{\rCHT}世界上威力最強的手槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.35,0:33:26.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm not Clint Eastwood. I'm Bruce Nolan.\N{\rCHT}我不是克林特·伊斯特伍德... 我是布魯斯·諾蘭!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.39,0:33:28.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm Bruce Nolan!\N{\rCHT}布魯斯·諾蘭... 布魯斯·諾蘭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.66,0:33:44.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That was not real.\N{\rCHT}這不是真的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.79,0:33:49.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Coffee? - Coffee, yeah.\N{\rCHT}- 要咖啡嗎? - 好... 咖啡... 好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.62,0:33:51.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We have a special on soup today.\N{\rCHT}我們今天有特色湯點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.71,0:33:55.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- No, thank you. - It's tomato. I made it myself.\N{\rCHT}- 不用 夠了 謝謝... - 是番茄湯 我親手做的哦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.34,0:33:59.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,OK.\N{\rCHT}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.12,0:34:35.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Excuse me, I need a spoo - ...\N{\rCHT}對不起... 我要只勺... 子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.43,0:34:44.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's OK. I found one.\N{\rCHT}不需要了 我找到了一隻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.89,0:34:53.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Here's your soup.\N{\rCHT}你的湯來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.77,0:34:55.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, soup, right.\N{\rCHT}噢... 湯... 好的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.48,0:34:57.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, right.\N{\rCHT}好的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.07,0:35:49.16,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Having fun?\N{\rCHT}很好玩吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.70,0:35:53.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thy, thou...\N{\rCHT}你...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.41,0:35:56.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come. Take a closer walk with me.\N{\rCHT}來 我們出去走走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.83,0:36:00.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Let me explain the rules. - Rules?\N{\rCHT}- 我來解釋一下規則 - 規則?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.17,0:36:03.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You left in such a rush, I didn't get a chance to explain.\N{\rCHT}是啊 你走得太快了 我還沒來得及解釋呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.34,0:36:08.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The two extra fingers freaked me out a little.\N{\rCHT}突然多出兩隻手指 嚇得我要死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.55,0:36:11.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I figured I'd get your attention.\N{\rCHT}我只是想引起你的注意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.10,0:36:14.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I did the same to Gandhi. He didn't eat for three weeks.\N{\rCHT}我對甘地也這麼做過... 他為此絕食了三個星期{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.43,0:36:17.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Anyway, here's the deal.\N{\rCHT}總之... 聽好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.35,0:36:20.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You have all my powers. Use them any way you choose.\N{\rCHT}你有我所有的神力 你可以以你選擇的方式任意使用{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.52,0:36:23.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There are two rules. You can't tell anybody you're God.\N{\rCHT}只有兩條規則 你不能告訴任何人你是上帝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.82,0:36:28.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Believe me, you don't want the attention. And you can't mess with free will.\N{\rCHT}相信我 你會為之後悔的 而且你不能干涉自主意志{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.91,0:36:35.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Can I ask why? - Yes! You can!\N{\rCHT}- 我可以問為什麼嗎? - 可以!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.37,0:36:37.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's the beauty of it.\N{\rCHT}這正是它的動人之處!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.84,0:36:48.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- This is amazing. - Speaking of amazing, excuse me.\N{\rCHT}- 這太神奇了 - 說到神奇... 讓讓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.01,0:36:55.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Holy sh - ... Cow.\N{\rCHT}王八... 牛啊!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.73,0:36:58.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Since you're through with these, I'll keep them.\N{\rCHT}既然你不要它 我就先幫你保管{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.31,0:37:01.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Might come in handy some day.\N{\rCHT}說不定某天會回到你手上的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.40,0:37:04.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,See you around, kid.\N{\rCHT}回見 小子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.94,0:37:08.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Where are you going? - I'm... taking a vacation.\N{\rCHT}- 你要去哪兒? - 我... 去度假{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.57,0:37:10.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,God doesn't take vacations.\N{\rCHT}上帝不是不度假的嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.45,0:37:12.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Does he? Do... ye?\N{\rCHT}現在可以? 以前也可以?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.03,0:37:15.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Did you ever hear of the Dark Ages?\N{\rCHT}你聽說過暗之世紀嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.45,0:37:19.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm covered. You can clear everything up in five minutes if you want.\N{\rCHT}而且 我有你頂著 如果你高興的話 5分鐘就可以搞定啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.79,0:37:21.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Right?\N{\rCHT}對不?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.59,0:38:09.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And he saw that it was good.\N{\rCHT}這種感覺就是爽啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.91,0:38:38.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,B - E - A - utiful!\N{\rCHT}潑... 伊... 傲... 漂亮!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.83,0:38:45.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Check it out.\N{\rCHT}看啊! 看啊!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.63,0:38:49.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Look, it's the hero.\N{\rCHT}看 這不是英雄兄嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.59,0:38:52.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Whassup, homie? - Yo, brethren, what up with thee?\N{\rCHT}- 你還好嗎? 諸位兄弟們 - 真是不走運啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.76,0:38:57.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Blessings on your alley. - Want another can of whup ass?\N{\rCHT}- 祝福降臨到你們這條巷子裡了 - 你又活得不耐煩了嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.51,0:39:00.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You didn't get enough? - He wants some more!\N{\rCHT}- 你還沒爽夠嗎 英雄先生? - 他真的沒爽夠!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.89,0:39:05.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Surely, I say unto you dudes, I do not wish to fight.\N{\rCHT}聽好了 小子們 我並不想打架{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.10,0:39:09.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,So as soon as you apologize and make a reckoning of your transgressions,\N{\rCHT}如果你們立即道歉 並且從此改邪歸正{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.36,0:39:13.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I shall absolve you and continue along the path of righteousness.\N{\rCHT}我就寬恕你們 大家各走各的路{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.57,0:39:15.66,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What are you talking about?\N{\rCHT}你在說什麼啊?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.78,0:39:20.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You talk kind of funny.\N{\rCHT}你真的很有意思 不過我也真的不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.38,0:39:22.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't know if you lost it up here or what.\N{\rCHT}你的腦袋裡是不是少了點什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.29,0:39:25.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You want me and the homies to apologize? Cool.\N{\rCHT}你要我們道歉是嗎? 沒問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.58,0:39:30.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We'll apologize the day a monkey comes out of my butt. How about that?\N{\rCHT}哪天我屁股裡要是鑽出只猴子來 我們就向你道歉 好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.97,0:39:37.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What a coincidence! Because that's today.\N{\rCHT}實在是太巧了! 因為那就是... 今天!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.20,0:39:57.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Did that monkey just come out your crack?\N{\rCHT}剛剛是不是有只猴子從你屁眼裡鑽出來?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.50,0:40:06.00,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is some voodoo shit!\N{\rCHT}- 巫術! - 魔鬼啊! 逃命啊!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.50,0:40:08.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You guys leaving?\N{\rCHT}怎麼就走啦?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.88,0:40:11.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget your parting gifts!\N{\rCHT}我還有禮物要送給你們哦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.12,0:40:41.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey, little anal - dwelling butt monkey.\N{\rCHT}屁股裡蹦出來的的小猴子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.87,0:40:44.66,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Time for you to go home.\N{\rCHT}你該回去了 小朋友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.88,0:41:00.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I am Bruce Almighty.\N{\rCHT}我就是全能的布魯斯!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.39,0:41:03.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,My will be done!\N{\rCHT}心想事成!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.52,0:41:16.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What if God was one of us\N{\rCHT}如果上帝就在我們之中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.40,0:41:20.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Just a slob like one of us\N{\rCHT}只是我們之中的一條懶漢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.03,0:41:23.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Just a stranger on a bus\N{\rCHT}只是公車上的一個陌生人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.70,0:41:25.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Trying to make his way\N{\rCHT}正在歸家...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.75,0:41:30.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Home\N{\rCHT}歸家的路上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.21,0:41:32.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- My God. - Call me Bruce.\N{\rCHT}- 上帝啊 - 你可以稱呼我為布魯斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.34,0:41:34.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What happened to you? You seem so...\N{\rCHT}你怎麼了 這麼這麼...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.47,0:41:40.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,happy.\N{\rCHT}... 開心?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.97,0:41:43.64,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Why shouldn't I be? On a night like this.\N{\rCHT}我有什麼理由不開心呢? 在這樣的夜晚裡...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.72,0:41:46.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Those are amazing. What are these?\N{\rCHT}好漂亮! 這是什麼花?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.68,0:41:50.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A new breed. A cross - pollination between tulips and daisies.\N{\rCHT}這是新品種 由鬱金香和雛菊雜交而成{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.35,0:41:53.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I call them todayzees.\N{\rCHT}我稱之為郁金菊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.69,0:41:56.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,OK.\N{\rCHT}好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.70,0:42:05.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Honey, these flowers are beautiful.\N{\rCHT}親愛的 這些花真是太漂亮了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.87,0:42:08.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- But last night... - Last night, I was only human.\N{\rCHT}- 昨晚... - 昨晚我還是個凡夫俗子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.00,0:42:16.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Barry, help me out.\N{\rCHT}貝裡 幫幫忙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.23,0:43:16.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Honey? Hi.\N{\rCHT}嗨 親愛的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.06,0:43:20.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I've never seen the moon that big. - Yeah.\N{\rCHT}- 我從沒見過這麼大的月亮! - 是啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.32,0:43:23.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We really shouldn't waste it.\N{\rCHT}我們可不能虛度了這迷人的月夜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.04,0:43:36.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Bedroom?\N{\rCHT}在臥室做?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.13,0:43:38.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Five minutes.\N{\rCHT}等我五分鐘!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.22,0:43:49.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Let there be light.\N{\rCHT}燭光!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.60,0:43:54.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll be out in a minute!\N{\rCHT}還有一分鐘!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.44,0:43:57.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't rush.\N{\rCHT}別急...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.27,0:44:00.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sometimes anticipation can heighten the...\N{\rCHT}有時候慢慢來反而會更有...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.40,0:44:01.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,pleasure!\N{\rCHT}快感!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.61,0:44:03.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, God.\N{\rCHT}哦 上帝啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.70,0:44:08.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's a funny thing about pleasure.\N{\rCHT}快感難以言表...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.99,0:44:14.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It can be quite... pleasurable!\N{\rCHT}它可以變成... 超快感!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.00,0:44:19.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, my God.\N{\rCHT}噢 上帝啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.75,0:44:21.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Pleasuring, pleasurable.\N{\rCHT}快感快感 快感快感...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.09,0:44:26.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, good God!\N{\rCHT}快感快感...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.27,0:44:38.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,In international news:\N{\rCHT}現在報告國際新聞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.27,0:44:42.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Japanese relief workers are staging an effort to rescue hundreds of people\N{\rCHT}日本救護人員正在搶救{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.57,0:44:46.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,stranded by a freak tidal wave that hit Kitamoto City.\N{\rCHT}被北本市的奇怪潮汐擱淺的數百名遊客...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.15,0:44:48.91,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Scientists say the tsunami may have been caused\N{\rCHT}科學家說這種現象可能是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.99,0:44:53.16,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,by what they are describing as unusual lunar activity.\N{\rCHT}由他們所說的"反常的月球運動"造成的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.24,0:44:55.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,More on this as it develops.\N{\rCHT}"進一步情況有待瞭解"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.17,0:45:04.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Please bless my mommy, my daddy, and especially my little sister.\N{\rCHT}"請保佑我的媽媽 爸爸 還有我的妹妹... "{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.97,0:45:09.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Please help me, Lord. Please get me through this one.\N{\rCHT}"請幫幫我 主啊 請幫我度過這難關... "{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.43,0:45:19.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you for everything else in my life. Amen.\N{\rCHT}"感謝您賜予我生命中的這一切 阿門"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.38,0:45:47.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Good boy.\N{\rCHT}好孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.30,0:45:51.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Forget something?\N{\rCHT}忘了什麼嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.64,0:45:57.52,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Good boy! There are girls in the house.\N{\rCHT}乖狗... 家裡有女生的哦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.90,0:46:03.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Morning. - Good morning.\N{\rCHT}- 早 - 早上好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.07,0:46:07.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I made you grilled cheese. - My favi.\N{\rCHT}- 我給你做了芝士三文治 - 噢 我的最愛!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.11,0:46:11.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Honey, last night was... - Heavenly. I know.\N{\rCHT}- 昨晚我... - 像上天堂? 我知道 我知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.61,0:46:16.20,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I mean, I woke up and I felt like my boobs were bigger.\N{\rCHT}我是說... 今天早上我一覺醒來 發現... 好像... 我的咪咪變大了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.29,0:46:19.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Do they look bigger to you? - What?\N{\rCHT}- 你覺得呢? 是不是大了? - 什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.50,0:46:21.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No.\N{\rCHT}噢...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.71,0:46:24.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Bigger? - Oh, come on!\N{\rCHT}- 變大了嗎? 沒有吧... - 拜託! 看看它們啊!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.38,0:46:26.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Look at them.\N{\rCHT}看嘛...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.25,0:46:28.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Please. They are definitely bigger.\N{\rCHT}絕對是變大了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.59,0:46:31.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I mean, look. They feel huge to me.\N{\rCHT}簡直是碩大無比 對我而言{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.34,0:46:33.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I have to go.\N{\rCHT}瞧 我得出門了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.34,0:46:35.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But this has been the breast bek...\N{\rCHT}這早餐真好...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.93,0:46:39.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you.\N{\rCHT}謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.31,0:46:42.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Where are you going? - To get my job back.\N{\rCHT}- 你要去哪兒? - 去把我的工作搶回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.19,0:46:48.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, yeah, I am great\N{\rCHT}我真行 我真好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.20,0:46:54.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Good grief! Is that what I'm driving?\N{\rCHT}好啊! 這就是我的車?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.21,0:47:07.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Nice car, man.\N{\rCHT}好漂亮的車! 夥計!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.96,0:47:10.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, it gets me from A to B.\N{\rCHT}是的 這才能襯托我的身份{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.64,0:47:26.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Darn. All this horsepower and no room to gallop!\N{\rCHT}天呀 這兒有這麼多車 沒有路來飛馳?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.57,0:47:33.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hi - yo, Silver. Away!\N{\rCHT}銀駒! 沖啊!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.79,0:47:43.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I wouldn't want to be a fugitive\N{\rCHT}我肯定不想成為被漢克追捕的逃犯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.83,0:47:47.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,with Hank, Buffalo's number one police dog, on the job.\N{\rCHT}水牛鎮警方的首席警犬正在演習{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.96,0:47:51.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Phil Sidleman at the police canine training center,\N{\rCHT}這是菲莉·西蒙 正在員警的訓練中心為你報導{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.28,0:47:52.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Channel 5 News.\N{\rCHT}這是第五頻道新聞節目{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.72,0:47:54.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And cut it.\N{\rCHT}可以停了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.39,0:48:01.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Look what the cat coughed up!\N{\rCHT}瞧瞧這是誰呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.06,0:48:05.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Channel 7, right? You're the guy that went crazy.\N{\rCHT}是第7頻道的 對嗎? 是那個發瘋的傢伙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.14,0:48:08.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I had a bad moment. - What are you doing here?\N{\rCHT}- 我那段時間很揹運 - 你來這裡幹什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.52,0:48:10.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Looking for a story. - No story here.\N{\rCHT}- 來找新聞 - 這裡沒有新聞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.82,0:48:15.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This pond is all fished out. Pretty standard stuff, anyway.\N{\rCHT}這池塘的魚都釣完了 一流的素材{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.45,0:48:18.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,My instinct tells me there's something more.\N{\rCHT}我不知道 我的直覺告訴我還有事發生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.87,0:48:21.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, go with that. It served you well in the past, right?\N{\rCHT}那就繼續堅持吧 以前你的直覺也不錯吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.25,0:48:32.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hank found something!\N{\rCHT}嘿 漢克發現了些東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.92,0:48:36.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We got a body!\N{\rCHT}我們找到了具屍體!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.01,0:48:39.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Shit. Get the camera! Now!\N{\rCHT}去拿攝像機! 立刻!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.89,0:48:43.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- It's locked! The keys are inside! - I guess every dog has his day.\N{\rCHT}- 鎖住了! 鑰匙在裡面! - 我想這就是風水輪流轉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.23,0:48:46.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Kid, you want to make $10? - Sure.\N{\rCHT}- 小子 想賺10塊錢嗎? - 當然{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.69,0:48:49.20,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Know how to use one of these? - Duh.\N{\rCHT}- 你會用這個吧? - 不會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.16,0:48:53.66,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Seems to be in tune. Let's do this.\N{\rCHT}看來沒有走調 我們來吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.74,0:48:56.87,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The body of Jimmy Hoffa was uncovered in a field today\N{\rCHT}吉米·霍夫曼的屍體今天在紐約市水牛鎮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.95,0:49:00.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,outside a canine training center in Buffalo, New York.\N{\rCHT}附近的訓練中心的一處草坪被發現{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.21,0:49:03.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Bruce Nolan was first on the scene. - Thank you, Jane.\N{\rCHT}- 布魯斯·諾蘭是第一個趕到現場的人 - 謝謝 簡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.92,0:49:07.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,As you can see, the body is being carefully exhumed\N{\rCHT}大家可以見到就在我身後 該屍體正被仔細地挖掘出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.21,0:49:11.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,for transportation to a facility where DNA can confirm the identity.\N{\rCHT}然後會被送到法醫處進行DNA鑒定 以確定身份{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.84,0:49:14.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That, however, merely a formality at this point,\N{\rCHT}不過 這一切只不過是手續而已{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.93,0:49:17.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,as the body was found with\N{\rCHT}因為在屍體旁奇跡般的發現了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.69,0:49:20.64,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,a birth certificate and dental records.\N{\rCHT}與案件相關的檔和死者的牙醫記錄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.73,0:49:23.52,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'd call that a red - letter day for any canine unit.\N{\rCHT}我想今天是適宜掘屍的吉日{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.61,0:49:26.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But was that enough for Hank? No, siree.\N{\rCHT}不過這對漢克來說還不算什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.40,0:49:29.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Moments later, he busted a local news camera crew\N{\rCHT}因為發現屍體之後不久 它還發現一輛本地媒體的採訪車上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.86,0:49:33.20,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,with 220 pounds of marijuana.\N{\rCHT}裝有100公斤的大麻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.28,0:49:35.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I never saw it before! I swear!\N{\rCHT}我沒有見過這東西! 我發誓!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.08,0:49:41.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm Bruce Nolan...\N{\rCHT}這裡是布魯斯·諾蘭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.21,0:49:44.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,and that's the way the cookie crumbles.\N{\rCHT}曲奇... 是這樣吃的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.76,0:49:50.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Did you like that?\N{\rCHT}你覺得怎麼樣?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.26,0:49:55.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you, thank you.\N{\rCHT}謝謝 謝謝!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.26,0:49:57.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Hi, Bruce. - Hi, Susan.\N{\rCHT}- 嗨 布魯斯 - 嗨 蘇姍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.35,0:49:59.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Good work. I'm impressed.\N{\rCHT}幹得好 你令我刮目相看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.02,0:50:06.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Did you need me for something? - Bruce!\N{\rCHT}- 傑克 要我做點什麼事嗎? - 布魯斯 布魯斯!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.07,0:50:09.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Just the man I want to see.\N{\rCHT}我正要找你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.19,0:50:13.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Hoffa? What are the odds of that? - What are the odds of that?\N{\rCHT}- 霍夫曼... 那事的反應如何? - 什麼是... 什麼反應如何...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.53,0:50:15.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Bruce, why don't you sit down? - OK.\N{\rCHT}- 布魯斯 請坐 - 好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.78,0:50:19.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm going to be straight with you. We want you back, Bruce.\N{\rCHT}我打算開門見山地和你談談 我們想要你回來 布魯斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.66,0:50:23.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But I want you to understand it was not my decision to let you go.\N{\rCHT}但我想要你明白的是 炒你魷魚的決定不是我做的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.92,0:50:26.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- When the big guy gives the order... - No harm, no foul.\N{\rCHT}- 是幕後的大人物下的命令 你知道的... - 不用擁抱 不用道歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.04,0:50:30.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I needed to reassess my goals and get in touch with my true self.\N{\rCHT}我需要時間重新設定我真正想做的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.80,0:50:33.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You did that in a day? - Imagine what I could do with seven.\N{\rCHT}- 給你一天節目時間 如何? - 我想我有能力做7天的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.13,0:50:38.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It is not in my power to give you anchor.\N{\rCHT}你知道的 布魯斯 我沒有權力給你主持人的職位{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.14,0:50:41.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,As far as field reporting goes, if you're looking for a bump...\N{\rCHT}只需要繼續有新聞 如果你想得到升遷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.68,0:50:44.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's cut the crap and get down to brass tacks.\N{\rCHT}傑克 我們廢話少說 我們開誠佈公吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.82,0:50:51.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I had you going.\N{\rCHT}你 看你的樣子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.69,0:50:53.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't worry about it, my old friend.\N{\rCHT}別擔心 老朋友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.86,0:50:57.66,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Just give me a camera. I'll give you the news.\N{\rCHT}只要你給我攝像機 傑克 我會給你新聞的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.67,0:51:12.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,My secret is that I let the jalapenos marinate in a spicy sauce\N{\rCHT}我的秘訣是就在於可以把特殊的味道融入到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.17,0:51:16.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,for at least 24 hours before I stir it into the chilli.\N{\rCHT}一種非常美味的菜汁中 然後等24小時後 我才開始製作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.51,0:51:19.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Then I let it all come to a simmer.\N{\rCHT}我將所有的東西都放在一個鍋裡...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.23,0:51:29.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hold that thought. It seems as if an asteroid or meteorite\N{\rCHT}留在這裡 夫人 你們看到了嗎? 一個小行星 或是某種隕星{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.73,0:51:33.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,has just hit ground right outside the Mark Twain Chilli Cook - Off!\N{\rCHT}剛剛墜落地面 就在... 馬克吐溫市場美食節現場外面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.32,0:51:36.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This should certainly spice things up a bit!\N{\rCHT}這將是你見過得最熱辣的東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.57,0:51:39.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,His stories are all over town.\N{\rCHT}這是全城的歷史時刻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.45,0:51:40.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,From unearthing Hoffa\N{\rCHT}自從發現了吉米·霍夫曼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.87,0:51:42.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,..to a meteor crashing,\N{\rCHT}到流星的墜落{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.04,0:51:46.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,..Bruce Nolan is rapidly becoming known as...\N{\rCHT}布魯斯·諾蘭 已經成為了 獨家新聞先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.10,0:52:04.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And that's the way the cookie crumbles!\N{\rCHT}水牛鎮曲奇就是這樣製成的!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.35,0:52:11.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This was Bruce's idea?\N{\rCHT}這是布魯斯的主意嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.90,0:52:16.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He wanted me to have a day of beauty and luxurious serenity.\N{\rCHT}他說要我做一整天的美容 豪華而舒適{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.07,0:52:21.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I got to tell you, he is impressing me lately.\N{\rCHT}我要告訴你 最近他令我刮目相看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.53,0:52:23.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Know where he's taking me to dinner?\N{\rCHT}你知道他今天要帶我去哪裡共進晚餐?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.08,0:52:26.87,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Where?\N{\rCHT}去哪裡?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.71,0:52:30.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The Blue Palm?\N{\rCHT}藍棕櫚飯店?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.25,0:52:35.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- My gosh, I got chills. - I know.\N{\rCHT}- 啊我的天 他抓住你 - 我知道...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.38,0:52:39.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He told me to prepare for the most memorable night of our lives.\N{\rCHT}他說 為你一生都會記住的一晚 做好準備{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.34,0:52:42.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, my gosh. He's going to propose.\N{\rCHT}我的老天 格雷斯 他想求婚了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.18,0:52:44.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, stop it. No. He's...\N{\rCHT}別說了...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.31,0:52:47.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Really? - Yeah, really.\N{\rCHT}- 真的? - 是的 別這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.18,0:52:50.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Do the math. He sends you all day to a beauty spa,\N{\rCHT}你想想 他讓你來美容院一整天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.40,0:52:54.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,he's taking you to a restaurant where you had your first date. Hello!\N{\rCHT}你們去那間本城最浪漫的飯店 你們第一次見面就在那裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.52,0:52:57.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I never thought I'd say this, but Bruce is right.\N{\rCHT}我認為將這個說成一次求婚是不正確的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.36,0:52:59.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is your night. Relax and enjoy it.\N{\rCHT}這是重要的一晚上 讓我們好好享受!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.74,0:53:01.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, God.\N{\rCHT}老天呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.04,0:53:09.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Welcome to Eyewitness News at Six, with Susan Ortega,\N{\rCHT}歡迎收看6點鐘新聞 主持人包括蘇珊·奧爾特加{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.62,0:53:11.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Evan Baxter,\N{\rCHT}埃文·巴克斯特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.12,0:53:13.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Fred Donohue, sports, Dallas Coleman, weather.\N{\rCHT}佛瑞德... 體育節目 達拉斯·科爾曼... 時事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.00,0:53:16.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And now, Buffalo's number one news team.\N{\rCHT}現在 這裡是水牛鎮第一新聞報導組{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.46,0:53:18.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Welcome to Eyewitness News at Six.\N{\rCHT}晚安 歡迎收看6點鐘新聞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.59,0:53:20.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I'm Susan Ortega. - I'm Evan Baxter.\N{\rCHT}- 我是蘇珊.奧爾特加 - 我是埃文·巴克斯特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.76,0:53:22.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Here's what's making news.\N{\rCHT}今天的新聞是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.89,0:53:26.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A potential scandal with the Buffalo PD surfaced today,\N{\rCHT}令人懷疑的水牛鎮警方醜聞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.35,0:53:28.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,when the mayor demanded that...\N{\rCHT}當市長...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.60,0:53:32.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,When the mayor demanded the chief of...\N{\rCHT}當市長...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.90,0:53:36.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Issued a response to...\N{\rCHT}對不起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.73,0:53:40.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I seem to have something stuck in my...\N{\rCHT}有東西噎住了了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.11,0:53:42.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Get him some water.\N{\rCHT}給他點水喝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.16,0:53:44.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Looks like my new co - anchor may need water.\N{\rCHT}看起來 我的搭檔需要杯水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.83,0:53:51.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There we go. Sorry.\N{\rCHT}好了 對剛才的事很抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.83,0:53:56.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,In other news, the prime minister of Sweden visited Washington today,\N{\rCHT}另一條新聞是 瑞典首相今天訪問華盛頓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.88,0:54:00.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,and my tiny little nipples went to France.\N{\rCHT}還有我的小情人去了法國{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.92,0:54:03.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What did he say? Check the prompter.\N{\rCHT}他在胡說什麼? 檢查下電子提示器{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.68,0:54:09.52,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- The prompter's fine. - Evan, read the copy.\N{\rCHT}- 提示器是好的 - 埃文 請跟著文本讀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.60,0:54:11.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The copy's good. Just read it.\N{\rCHT}文本沒有問題 照著讀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.10,0:54:15.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The White House committee greeted the prime rib roast minister,\N{\rCHT}白宮會議通過了首相的提議{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.94,0:54:19.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,and I do the cha - cha like a sissy girl.\N{\rCHT}還有我像個女人般地跳喳喳舞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.11,0:54:23.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I lika do...\N{\rCHT}我喜歡... 跳...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.95,0:54:25.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,da cha - cha.\N{\rCHT}喳喳舞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.20,0:54:34.00,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm sorry. We seem to be having technical difficulties.\N{\rCHT}抱歉 看起來我們好像有點技術問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.37,0:54:36.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,In other news...\N{\rCHT}另一條新聞是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.21,0:54:41.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,My apologies.\N{\rCHT}對不起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.38,0:56:07.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- May I? - Certainly.\N{\rCHT}- 可以嗎? - 當然{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.89,0:56:15.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's perfect. She'll love it.\N{\rCHT}太完美了 她應該會喜歡的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.56,0:56:26.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You know, I was going to wait until after the meal,\N{\rCHT}你知道嗎? 我將... 我終於揚眉吐氣了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.24,0:56:30.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,but it'll burst out of me like an alien if I don't do it now.\N{\rCHT}他們再也不能把我當白癡了 我不會讓他們這麼做的了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.37,0:56:34.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, my God. OK.\N{\rCHT}老天 沒事的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.58,0:56:36.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is it, isn't it?\N{\rCHT}會發生什麼事?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.45,0:56:39.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't know if I'm ready for this.\N{\rCHT}我不知道 我還沒準備好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.42,0:56:44.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I mean, I'm ready. I just didn't know if I would... I'm sorry, go on.\N{\rCHT}我不是說我還沒準備好 我只是有點緊張 對不起 繼續說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.42,0:56:47.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I didn't know it was so important to you. - Me neither.\N{\rCHT}- 我不知道這對你會有多重要 - 我也不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.93,0:56:54.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Grace? - Yes?\N{\rCHT}- 格雷斯 - 好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.90,0:57:03.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I got anchor.\N{\rCHT}我成為主持人了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.73,0:57:06.15,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No.\N{\rCHT}噢...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.78,0:57:11.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes. Apparently it wasn't working out with Evan,\N{\rCHT}是的 他們要辭掉埃文{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.07,0:57:16.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,so he's going to finish out the week and I go live on Monday.\N{\rCHT}這周他就要走人 星期一我就要上任了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.50,0:57:22.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- That's great, honey. - I know, I know.\N{\rCHT}- 太好了 親愛的 - 我知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.50,0:57:24.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Well...\N{\rCHT}那麼...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.50,0:57:29.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- So that's what this is all about. - Well, yeah.\N{\rCHT}- 就是為了這些事情嗎? - 是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.88,0:57:32.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We got anchor.\N{\rCHT}格雷斯 我是主持人了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.47,0:57:36.14,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Jack's throwing me a party at the Vanderbilt estate to celebrate.\N{\rCHT}傑克星期五要凱歌晚會為我慶祝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.22,0:57:38.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What's the matter? - Nothing.\N{\rCHT}- 怎麼了? - 沒事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.77,0:57:42.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Now I lay me down to sleep...\N{\rCHT}我現在只想躺下睡覺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.15,0:57:44.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I feel stupid.\N{\rCHT}啊 我多笨呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.19,0:57:47.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- It is loud in here, isn't it? - No, it's not loud.\N{\rCHT}- 啊 這裡太吵了 不是嗎? - 不 這裡不吵{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.11,0:57:50.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Jeez! Can you keep it down to a dull roar?\N{\rCHT}你們能小聲點嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.53,0:57:53.16,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Thank you! - Is that supposed to be funny?\N{\rCHT}- 謝謝! - 這很搞笑嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.24,0:57:56.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Cos that is not funny.\N{\rCHT}這一點都不搞笑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.12,0:57:59.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What did you say? - What is wrong with you? Stop yelling.\N{\rCHT}- 你在說什麼? - 你怎麼了? 不要叫嚷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.91,0:58:05.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If you'll excuse me, I'll take a little trip to the...\N{\rCHT}對不起 我要出去...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.21,0:58:10.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The wine is going right through me.\N{\rCHT}那酒的作用 我有點醉了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.09,0:58:13.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.\N{\rCHT}對不起 真得很抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.43,0:58:15.64,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Keep going, Tony! - Oh, God.\N{\rCHT}- 繼續 托尼! 你很棒! - 噢 上帝!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.14,0:58:20.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What is going on here?\N{\rCHT}怎麼了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.14,0:58:22.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What is this?\N{\rCHT}這是怎麼回事?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.19,0:58:24.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Give me a break!\N{\rCHT}別來煩我!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.28,0:58:31.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Really something, isn't it?\N{\rCHT}非常吵雜 是不是?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.03,0:58:35.91,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Is this heaven?\N{\rCHT}這裡是天堂嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.99,0:58:38.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No, this is Mount Everest.\N{\rCHT}不是 這是珠穆朗瑪峰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.66,0:58:41.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Flip on the Discovery Channel from time to time.\N{\rCHT}你應該經常在探索頻道看到過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.16,0:58:45.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But I guess you can't now, being dead and all.\N{\rCHT}但我想你現在無法看到了 你已經死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.96,0:58:49.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I'm dead? - I'm just messing with you.\N{\rCHT}- 我死了嗎? - 沒有 只想忽悠你一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.42,0:58:53.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's not funny, man!\N{\rCHT}那並不好笑 夥計!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.13,0:58:58.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What about the voices in my head? Is that part of the hilarity?\N{\rCHT}我腦子裡的聲音是怎麼回事? 這也是笑話的一部分?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.01,0:59:01.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No, those are prayers. You keep ignoring them,\N{\rCHT}那些是禱告的人 你不斷地忽視他們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.78,0:59:03.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,they're going to build up.\N{\rCHT}他們就集聚在你的頭腦中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.48,0:59:06.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But it's just noise. I can't understand them.\N{\rCHT}那些只是些噪音 我無法弄明白的噪音{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.98,0:59:09.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You're not listening, son.\N{\rCHT}是你沒有留心聽 孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.82,0:59:12.15,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's see.\N{\rCHT}我們來看看吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.28,0:59:16.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You had my powers for a little over a week. How many people have you helped?\N{\rCHT}你擁有我能力的有一周了 你已幫助了多少人?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.58,0:59:22.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I took care of a few things.\N{\rCHT}我 我照管你的事情{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.70,0:59:25.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I righted a few wrongs in my own life first. OK?\N{\rCHT}無論這是對失錯 我得先管好自己的事 這排第一 行吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.04,0:59:28.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I was going to help the others.\N{\rCHT}然後我才會去幫助別人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.29,0:59:31.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I think I could help the world. - The world?\N{\rCHT}- 我想我有能力幫助全世界 - 全世界?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.01,0:59:36.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That wasn't the world. That was just Buffalo, between 57th and Commonwealth.\N{\rCHT}不用管全世界 只是水牛鎮 在57條街道之間的眾生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.05,0:59:43.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I didn't want to start you off with more than you could handle.\N{\rCHT}我只能給你 你的能力所及的工作給你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.52,0:59:46.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You took the job, Bruce, so I suggest you get to it.\N{\rCHT}既然你領了工作 我建議你開始工作吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.56,0:59:51.52,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Seeing him smile would make me so happy.\N{\rCHT}看到他的微笑會讓我高興萬分{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.61,0:59:53.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Prayers, prayers, OK.\N{\rCHT}禱告者們 禱告者們 好的 禱告者們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.07,0:59:57.20,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This creepy whisper thing has to end.\N{\rCHT}這些聲音令我難受!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.28,0:59:59.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Organization. That's what I need.\N{\rCHT}我需要的是有組織的 可以方便管理{\r}
