Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.58,1:02:12.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Good.\N{\rCHT}味道真不錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.71,1:02:20.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,OK, I had to have made some kind of a dent by now.\N{\rCHT}好的 我終於做完了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.05,1:02:25.14,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, come on!\N{\rCHT}啊 別這樣!{\r}
