Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.02,1:02:34.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You know what?\N{\rCHT}你懂什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.23,1:02:38.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes. To all.\N{\rCHT}同意! 給所有人!{\r}
