Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.63,1:03:49.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is Bruce, Grace and Sam. Leave a message.\N{\rCHT}這是布魯斯 格雷斯和薩姆 請留下口信{\r}
