Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.10,1:03:58.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on, Grace. Come to the party.\N{\rCHT}別這樣 格雷斯 來參加晚會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.23,1:04:01.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll call you later, OK?\N{\rCHT}我待會再給你電話 好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.61,1:04:05.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on, Sam.\N{\rCHT}快點 薩姆{\r}
