Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.29,1:04:56.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is Bruce, Grace and Sam.\N{\rCHT}這是布魯斯 格雷斯和薩姆...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.21,1:05:00.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hi, Bruce.\N{\rCHT}你好 布魯斯{\r}
