Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.51,1:05:08.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I mean...\N{\rCHT}我是說...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.05,1:05:13.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I was going to give Grace a call.\N{\rCHT}我只是... 等格雷斯的電話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.10,1:05:17.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, I didn't see her. So how are you and Grace doing?\N{\rCHT}是的 在那邊我沒有見到她 你和格雷斯相處得如何?{\r}
