Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.44,1:06:07.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Grace, come here!\N{\rCHT}格雷斯 過來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.61,1:06:10.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is weird. I was just calling you.\N{\rCHT}這太怪了 我當時正在給你電話...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.78,1:06:13.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And you thought Susan's mouth was the phone?\N{\rCHT}啊 你以為蘇珊的嘴是電話嗎?{\r}
