Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.13,1:06:31.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And maybe two big bags of cash.\N{\rCHT}或者兩大箱現金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.17,1:06:33.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Then, then, I'll be happy.\N{\rCHT}那我就會開心了{\r}
