Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.08,1:10:29.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's not food.\N{\rCHT}不要吃那東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.54,1:10:33.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Go to the bathroom. Wash out your mouth. Wash off your hands.\N{\rCHT}啊 這不好 去洗手間 清洗下你得嘴和雙手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.21,1:10:36.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That kid is gonna poop an ornament.\N{\rCHT}上帝呀 什麼都敢吃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.71,1:10:39.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,One more time, you're going to be in a lot of trouble.\N{\rCHT}再來一次的話 你就會有大麻煩!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.30,1:10:43.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, that's it!\N{\rCHT}好了! 這就是 這就是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.47,1:10:48.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I surrender!\N{\rCHT}我投降 我投降!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.27,1:10:56.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hi.\N{\rCHT}嗨!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.15,1:11:03.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm... doing my first anchor tonight.\N{\rCHT}我將... 今晚將第一次做主持人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.36,1:11:06.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, wow. That's great!\N{\rCHT}哇! 太好了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.37,1:11:10.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- How have you been doing? - Good.\N{\rCHT}- 你怎麼想? - 很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.96,1:11:15.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Debbie won the lottery. - Oh, yeah? You're kidding.\N{\rCHT}- 啊 黛比中了彩票 - 啊 是嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.50,1:11:17.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But so did 400, 000 other people,\N{\rCHT}他和40萬人一起中了獎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.52,1:11:21.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,so she only won like $17 or something.\N{\rCHT}所以她只得到17元{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.93,1:11:26.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I miss you.\N{\rCHT}我想念你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.02,1:11:32.77,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I took a first step.\N{\rCHT}好的 我主動點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.85,1:11:34.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Jumped out on a ledge.\N{\rCHT}先勾畫出框框{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.73,1:11:39.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Feeling vulnerable. - What do you want me to say?\N{\rCHT}- 你也相當悶 - 我不知道你想我說什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.73,1:11:41.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Say you want me back.\N{\rCHT}說你愛我 你想要我回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.03,1:11:44.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What about all the signs?\N{\rCHT}不 布魯斯 那些天邊的啟示表示什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.65,1:11:48.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How did you know about that? Did you talk to Debbie?\N{\rCHT}你怎麼知道那事的? 你同黛比談過了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.87,1:11:51.91,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Would it help if I just said I was a complete ass?\N{\rCHT}你願意幫忙告訴我 我是個大混...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.04,1:11:55.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You said ass! - It's OK if I'm talking about a donkey.\N{\rCHT}- 嘿 你說粗話 - 沒事的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.71,1:11:58.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I didn't say "hole". If I said ass...\N{\rCHT}我沒有說"蛋"字... 我說"混"...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.29,1:12:01.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No, wait. OK, honey, let's go inside.\N{\rCHT}孩子們 我們走! 去裡面!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.21,1:12:04.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, everybody inside. Time to go inside.\N{\rCHT}孩子們 大家都進去 該進去了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.55,1:12:09.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Please. None of this seems right without you.\N{\rCHT}格雷斯 求你了 沒了你一切都不對頭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.60,1:12:15.77,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I gotta go.\N{\rCHT}我得走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.23,1:12:17.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Wait!\N{\rCHT}等等!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.28,1:12:26.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How do you feel now?\N{\rCHT}你現在感覺任何?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.07,1:12:31.91,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Have you completely lost your mind?\N{\rCHT}你真得徹底... 瘋了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.29,1:12:35.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Are you drunk? - Yeah. Drunk with power.\N{\rCHT}- 還是喝醉了? - 我喝醉了 徹底醉了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.92,1:12:42.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Love me.\N{\rCHT}愛我!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.97,1:12:52.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I did.\N{\rCHT}我愛過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.07,1:13:06.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, I know. Free will.\N{\rCHT}好了 我知道了 自由的思想{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.49,1:13:11.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,More power outages reported today caused by last week's meteorite strike.\N{\rCHT}越來越多的停電的報告 因為上次隕星的墜落{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.08,1:13:16.00,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Officials are trying to repair transformers\N{\rCHT}有關方面疲於修復{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.00,1:13:18.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,damaged by the ensuing electrical surge.\N{\rCHT}隕星爆炸破壞的變壓器{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.37,1:13:20.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The scene nearly turned violent\N{\rCHT}現場變得失控{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.38,1:13:25.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,when Buffalo residents protested last week's lottery results.\N{\rCHT}當數百名水牛鎮居民 抗議上周的彩票結果{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.42,1:13:29.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Doomsayers are pointing to last week's strange celestial events\N{\rCHT}末日的恐懼和上周的奇怪的事情被人們視為{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.30,1:13:34.64,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,as signs that prophecy is being fulfilled and the world may be coming to an end.\N{\rCHT}預言就要實現的徵兆 現在的世界將終結{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.31,1:13:37.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The world's gone mad.\N{\rCHT}瘋了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.81,1:13:39.77,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 30 seconds to air. - OK.\N{\rCHT}- 布魯斯 30秒鐘 - 好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.85,1:13:42.77,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There you are. It's your debut. How are you feeling?\N{\rCHT}到你了 你的大日子 感覺如何?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.86,1:13:46.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You know what? I'm fine. Never better.\N{\rCHT}很好 從來沒有這麼好過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.61,1:13:48.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The show must go on right?\N{\rCHT}我們開始了 是嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.78,1:13:55.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- The Sabres just won the Stanley Cup. - You're kidding me!\N{\rCHT}- 剃刀隊剛剛贏史丹尼員警隊 - 你開玩笑嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.74,1:13:58.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Was that tonight? That's great.\N{\rCHT}是今晚嗎? 太好了 不是嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.54,1:14:03.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's crazy out there. We're going to kick live to Fred at the stadium, OK?\N{\rCHT}我們得直播在體育館的佛瑞德的情況 好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.13,1:14:05.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Five seconds to the open. - This is it.\N{\rCHT}還有5秒鐘開播{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.71,1:14:07.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You ready? - Born that way.\N{\rCHT}- 開始? 準備好了嗎? - 一直準備好的!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.80,1:14:13.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Welcome to Eyewitness News at Six, with Susan Ortega, Bruce Nolan,\N{\rCHT}歡迎收看6點鐘新聞 由蘇珊·奧爾特加 布魯斯·諾蘭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.39,1:14:16.14,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Fred Donohue, sports, Dallas Coleman, weather.\N{\rCHT}佛瑞德... 體育 達拉斯·科爾曼... 天氣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.22,1:14:18.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Now Buffalo's number one news team.\N{\rCHT}這裡是水牛鎮第一的新聞報導小組{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.31,1:14:20.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I'm Susan Ortega. - I'm Bruce Nolan.\N{\rCHT}- 我是蘇珊·奧爾特加 - 我是布魯斯·諾蘭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.48,1:14:22.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And here's what's making news.\N{\rCHT}今天的新聞是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.86,1:14:26.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What happened? - We lost power.\N{\rCHT}- 什麼事? - 停電了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.52,1:14:28.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Transformer's down again. - Jeez.\N{\rCHT}- 變壓器壞了 - 老天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.69,1:14:31.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Ever since that damn meteorite hit.\N{\rCHT}都是那該死的隕星{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.82,1:14:35.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- We're back. - We apologize for the interruption.\N{\rCHT}- 好了 有電了 - 我們為剛才的中斷抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.78,1:14:37.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Back to the news. Bruce? - Thank you.\N{\rCHT}- 現在開始報導新聞 布魯斯 - 謝謝 蘇珊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.08,1:14:41.16,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm sorry. We're going live to HSBC Arena,\N{\rCHT}對不起 我們現在要直播水牛鎮剃刀隊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.25,1:14:44.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,where the Buffalo Sabres have won the Stanley Cup.\N{\rCHT}所在的體育館的情況 他們剛剛贏了史丹尼員警隊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.46,1:14:45.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Great. - Fred?\N{\rCHT}- 太好了 - 佛瑞德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.92,1:14:48.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We're about to uncork some champagne because\N{\rCHT}我們準備開香檳 因為剃刀隊在這裡贏得了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.67,1:14:53.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,the Sabres have won their first championship in 22 years!\N{\rCHT}22年來的第一個冠軍...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.93,1:14:57.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What in blazes...\N{\rCHT}正中頭部{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.43,1:15:02.14,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We'll be back with the Sabres' victory in just a hot second.\N{\rCHT}我們一會再回到現場報導 很快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.23,1:15:04.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,In other news...\N{\rCHT}另一條新聞是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.15,1:15:06.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Bloody hell! - What is it now?\N{\rCHT}- 又來了? 怎麼回事? - 不 不是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.81,1:15:08.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- The whole booth is down. - It's not!\N{\rCHT}保險全壞了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.48,1:15:14.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,In other news, fighting erupted in the Gaza Strip today,\N{\rCHT}另一條新聞 衝突今天在加沙又起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.03,1:15:17.16,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,as Israelis and Palestinians...\N{\rCHT}巴勒斯坦人...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.24,1:15:18.66,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Bruce. - What?\N{\rCHT}- 布魯斯 - 什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.74,1:15:22.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We've got a situation here. They're rioting right outside.\N{\rCHT}本地有狀況 暴亂失控了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.16,1:15:25.00,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You're kidding. - The whole town has gone crazy.\N{\rCHT}- 別和我開玩笑了 - 全城都瘋了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.05,1:15:32.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Go on, Bruce. Say something.\N{\rCHT}布魯斯 說話呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.17,1:15:36.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Ladies and gentlemen, this just in.\N{\rCHT}女士們先生們 報導結束了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.26,1:15:42.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Possibly the biggest breaking news story this town has ever seen.\N{\rCHT}本城發生了也許是你從未見過的突發事件{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.94,1:15:52.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And I gotta go.\N{\rCHT}我得走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.86,1:15:54.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sorry, Jack.\N{\rCHT}對不起 傑克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.45,1:15:57.91,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Susan, it's all yours.\N{\rCHT}蘇珊 我對不起大家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.24,1:16:03.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sabres!\N{\rCHT}剃刀!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.50,1:16:05.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sabres rule!\N{\rCHT}剃刀隊是第一!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.83,1:16:08.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Down with the lottery!\N{\rCHT}終止博彩!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.33,1:16:10.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Repent! The end is near!\N{\rCHT}懺悔吧! 末日來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.81,1:16:26.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The lottery sucks!\N{\rCHT}博彩是騙局!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.10,1:16:29.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I only won 17 bucks!\N{\rCHT}只有17元{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.40,1:16:33.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Channel 7 lies!\N{\rCHT}第7頻道是騙子!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.28,1:16:37.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, no!\N{\rCHT}不!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.13,1:16:51.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,God!\N{\rCHT}上帝呀!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.92,1:16:56.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,God?\N{\rCHT}上帝?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.80,1:16:58.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you here?\N{\rCHT}你在嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.60,1:17:04.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hello? I need your help!\N{\rCHT}你好! 我需要幫助!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.72,1:17:07.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Clap on!\N{\rCHT}鼓掌 鼓掌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.49,1:17:17.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Figures!\N{\rCHT}快點出現吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.70,1:17:23.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, hello there, Bruce Almighty.\N{\rCHT}我就知道! 那邊的 你好 全能的布魯斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.45,1:17:30.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Not as easy as it looks, is it, son? This God business.\N{\rCHT}看起來很容易 不是嗎 孩子? 上帝的工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.38,1:17:33.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,They're all out of control.\N{\rCHT}一切都失控了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.05,1:17:36.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's me. I don't know what to do.\N{\rCHT}他們瘋了 我束手無策{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.76,1:17:39.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, you're right on time. Seven o'clock.\N{\rCHT}你來得很準時 7點鐘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.72,1:17:44.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The 7th at 7.00.\N{\rCHT}7點 到7點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.40,1:18:01.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,All righty, then.\N{\rCHT}啊 做完了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.87,1:18:06.83,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- There we are. - It's good.\N{\rCHT}- 就到這裡 - 不錯 不錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.12,1:18:10.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's a wonderful thing.\N{\rCHT}了不起的事情{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.83,1:18:15.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No matter how filthy something gets, you can always clean it right up.\N{\rCHT}無論搞得多亂 我們總能清理好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.75,1:18:20.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There were so many. I just gave them all what they wanted.\N{\rCHT}他們有太多的要求了 我只能滿足他們的需要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.30,1:18:21.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}是啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.55,1:18:26.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But since when does anyone have a clue about what they want?\N{\rCHT}那麼是你在什麼時候有了線索... 什麼是他們所需要的呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.98,1:18:31.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,So what do I do?\N{\rCHT}那麼我該怎麼做?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.11,1:18:36.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Parting your soup is not a miracle.\N{\rCHT}分開一盆濃湯並不是什麼奇跡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.35,1:18:38.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's a magic trick.\N{\rCHT}那只是一個小小的魔術把戲而已{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.19,1:18:41.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A single mom who's working two jobs\N{\rCHT}一位單身媽媽 每天要打兩份工{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.86,1:18:45.91,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,and still finds time to take her kid to soccer practice, that's a miracle.\N{\rCHT}但還是能抽的出時間陪孩子參加足球練習 那才是一種奇跡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.33,1:18:49.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A teenager who says no to drugs and yes to an education,\N{\rCHT}年輕人說要遠離毒品 而且要努力受教育{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.66,1:18:52.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,that's a miracle.\N{\rCHT}這也是一種奇跡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.54,1:18:55.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,People want me to do everything for them.\N{\rCHT}人們要求我為他們實現任何他們自己的願望{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.00,1:18:59.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What they don't realize is they have the power.\N{\rCHT}但是他們從來沒有意識到 他們自己具有實現自己願望的能力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.42,1:19:03.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You want to see a miracle, son?\N{\rCHT}年輕人 想要看到真正的奇跡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.22,1:19:05.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Be the miracle.\N{\rCHT}首先得要自己努力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.64,1:19:10.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Wait. Are you leaving?\N{\rCHT}等一下 你要走了嘛?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.35,1:19:14.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah. I figure you can handle things now.\N{\rCHT}是啊! 我想你現在可以自己解決問題了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.27,1:19:15.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But what if I need you?\N{\rCHT}但如果我又需要你説明{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.47,1:19:17.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What if I have questions?\N{\rCHT}或者我又有別的問題的時候怎麼辦?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.15,1:19:19.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's your problem, Bruce.\N{\rCHT}這就是你的問題嘍 布魯斯!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.65,1:19:21.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's everybody's problem.\N{\rCHT}這也是我們每個人的問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.78,1:19:23.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You keep looking up.\N{\rCHT}你要繼續留神嘍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.70,1:19:31.91,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Order has been restored after this evening's downtown riot.\N{\rCHT}在今天的示威遊行之後 水牛鎮本地的秩序已經恢復正常{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.00,1:19:34.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,State officials have suspended all lottery sales\N{\rCHT}官方已經終止了博彩的銷售{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.87,1:19:36.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,pending further investigation.\N{\rCHT}正在尋找妥善的解決方法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.00,1:19:41.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No injuries were reported in the melee, however there were dozens of arrests.\N{\rCHT}這次示威遊行中沒有傷亡報告{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.68,1:20:31.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,OK.\N{\rCHT}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.68,1:20:34.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Thanks a million. - Not a problem.\N{\rCHT}- 萬分感謝 - 小意思{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.77,1:20:36.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,God bless.\N{\rCHT}上帝保佑你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.57,1:20:45.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Bruce giveth and Bruce... taketh away.\N{\rCHT}布魯斯給予你們的 布魯斯再次收回{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.82,1:20:48.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If you don't like it... mega - bite me.\N{\rCHT}你們要是不情願的話 來咬我吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.00,1:20:59.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Evan? - Bruce.\N{\rCHT}- 埃文 - 布魯斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.34,1:21:05.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I suppose you're here to gloat about\N{\rCHT}我想你是回來取代我的主持人身份的吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.05,1:21:07.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,the anchor position. Go ahead.\N{\rCHT}它們是你的了 作出你最好的報導吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.51,1:21:09.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, actually, I...\N{\rCHT}實際上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.85,1:21:14.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I just came to tell you that I've been a royal prick.\N{\rCHT}我是來告訴你 我放棄了從事主持方面的工作了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.27,1:21:17.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The anchor position is yours. I turned down the job.\N{\rCHT}位置給你留著 我辭掉了這份工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.98,1:21:20.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And I never really congratulated you.\N{\rCHT}對了! 我還沒有向你的祝賀呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.15,1:21:24.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Congratulations.\N{\rCHT}恭喜了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.53,1:21:28.15,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thanks, Bruce.\N{\rCHT}多謝了! 布魯斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.24,1:21:31.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,In the financial world, things are back to normal\N{\rCHT}目前的金融界 一切都歸於平常{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.32,1:21:34.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,in what analysts are calling a fluke market fluctuation.\N{\rCHT}我們稱其為 平衡的市場效應{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.62,1:21:37.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You made the right move. - What about you?\N{\rCHT}- 你這一步走得不錯! - 傑克? - 嗯! 那麼你準備怎麼樣?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.37,1:21:39.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You ready to go back out there?\N{\rCHT}準備繼續回到外面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.63,1:21:43.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Do the cutesy stuff? The lighter side of the news?\N{\rCHT}去捕捉新聞了嘛? 那些可愛的報導{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.54,1:21:47.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Lower and debase myself for the amusement of strangers?\N{\rCHT}我必須自降身價去取悅那些我都不認識的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.47,1:21:49.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, I could do that. Sounds like fun.\N{\rCHT}嗯! 是啊! 我可以做這些事情 聽上去蠻有趣的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.93,1:21:51.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Good.\N{\rCHT}不錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.26,1:21:55.64,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,OK, Sammy, let's do it right. Like all the other dogs.\N{\rCHT}好了 薩姆 我們現在就開始了 就像其他所有的狗一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.72,1:21:59.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't want to make you feel bad, but they're laughing at you, pal.\N{\rCHT}我不想你難受 放鬆 放鬆夥計{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.48,1:22:01.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on. Concentrate.\N{\rCHT}好! 就這樣 集中你的精神...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.77,1:22:04.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Pump it out, if you have to.\N{\rCHT}快點拉出來吧 如果你必須的話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.11,1:22:06.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What am I going to do with you?\N{\rCHT}天哪! 我要把你怎麼辦?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.90,1:22:11.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I know this seems kind of crazy,\N{\rCHT}我知道這可能看上去很瘋狂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.91,1:22:16.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,but desperate times call for desperate measures.\N{\rCHT}但是值得試試 解決你的問題吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.37,1:22:21.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,OK, Sammy. Do your thing.\N{\rCHT}好了 薩姆 你的東西來了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.96,1:22:25.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's it. Good boy!\N{\rCHT}就是這樣 就是這樣! 乖孩子!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.34,1:22:29.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Training my dog.\N{\rCHT}正在訓練我的狗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.82,1:22:52.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes! We did it!\N{\rCHT}太好了 我們成功了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.66,1:22:58.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We're doing it doggy style\N{\rCHT}你終於象狗一樣了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.41,1:23:01.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll alert Penthouse Forum.\N{\rCHT}我看你還是老樣子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.79,1:23:03.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hi, Deb. How are you?\N{\rCHT}你好黛比 還好嘛?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.71,1:23:06.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How's Grace?\N{\rCHT}格雷斯怎麼樣了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.17,1:23:07.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I didn't come to chat.\N{\rCHT}我不是來聊天的 布魯斯?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.59,1:23:09.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I came for Grace's stuff.\N{\rCHT}我是來拿格雷斯留在你這裡的東西的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.43,1:23:18.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You need a...? - That's OK. I've got it.\N{\rCHT}- 需要什麼... - 不了 我已經拿完了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.44,1:23:27.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't know if she...\N{\rCHT}我... 我不想她把它們賣掉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.44,1:23:29.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't know if she wants that or not.\N{\rCHT}我不知道她是否需要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.95,1:23:37.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is full. You did all this?\N{\rCHT}這裡插滿了啊! 都是你幹的嘛?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.92,1:23:50.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You know what I do before I go to bed?\N{\rCHT}你知道每天晚上我上床前做的事情嘛?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.42,1:23:54.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I tuck my kids in, maybe have some ice cream and watch Conan.\N{\rCHT}我帶著我的孩子 一起看看電影或者電視{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.09,1:23:58.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Know what Grace does?\N{\rCHT}想知道格雷斯會做什麼嘛?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.39,1:24:01.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,She prays.\N{\rCHT}她會祈禱上帝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.64,1:24:04.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Most of the time for you.\N{\rCHT}大部分時間都是為了你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.46,1:24:29.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Find Grace Connelly.\N{\rCHT}查找關鍵字語"格雷斯·康納利"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.63,1:24:34.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The woman does pray a lot.\N{\rCHT}喔! 女人真是會祈禱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.80,1:24:39.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Find... Grace and Bruce.\N{\rCHT}查找關鍵字語"格雷斯和布魯斯"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.68,1:24:43.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"Dear God, please help Bruce find himself,\N{\rCHT}親愛的上帝 請幫助布魯斯找回他自我吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.18,1:24:45.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,find contentment, find you."\N{\rCHT}讓他學會滿足{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.31,1:24:47.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"Dear God, please help Bruce.\N{\rCHT}親愛的上帝啊 請幫幫布魯斯吧!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.49,1:24:48.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He seems to be struggling."\N{\rCHT}他常常為了發現真相而掙扎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.98,1:24:51.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"Dear God, give Bruce strength."\N{\rCHT}親愛的上帝啊 賜予布魯斯力量吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.11,1:24:52.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"Dear God, bless Bruce."\N{\rCHT}親愛的上帝啊 請保佑布魯斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.78,1:24:59.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's her.\N{\rCHT}是她的願望!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.28,1:25:03.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sammy, she's logging on. She's praying right now.\N{\rCHT}她正登陸上來 正在祈禱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.88,1:25:12.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Please, God.\N{\rCHT}求你了 上帝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.30,1:25:15.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Please.\N{\rCHT}求你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.76,1:25:17.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I still love him.\N{\rCHT}我還愛著他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.22,1:25:23.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But I don't want to love him any more.\N{\rCHT}但是我不想再繼續愛他下去了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.31,1:25:25.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't want to hurt any more. Please.\N{\rCHT}我也不想再受到傷害了! 求你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.43,1:25:28.52,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Help me forget.\N{\rCHT}幫我忘記他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.27,1:25:31.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Please help me to let it go.\N{\rCHT}讓我可以忘了他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.52,1:25:34.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Please help me let him go.\N{\rCHT}求你了! 幫我離開他吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.96,1:25:58.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You win!\N{\rCHT}你贏了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.76,1:26:00.64,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm done!\N{\rCHT}我完了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.72,1:26:04.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Please! I don't want to do this any more!\N{\rCHT}我不想再幹這個了 求你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.52,1:26:07.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't want to be God.\N{\rCHT}我不想成為上帝了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.23,1:26:11.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I want you to decide what's right for me!\N{\rCHT}我想還是由你來決定我的人生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.81,1:26:14.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I surrender to your will!\N{\rCHT}我向你的意願認輸了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.93,1:26:46.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Am I...?\N{\rCHT}我是不是...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.39,1:26:50.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You can't kneel down in the middle of a highway and live to talk about it.\N{\rCHT}你不可以在高速公路的中間跪了下來 說自己還活著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.48,1:26:52.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But why?\N{\rCHT}為什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.81,1:26:55.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Why now?\N{\rCHT}為什麼現在...?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.57,1:26:57.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Bruce...\N{\rCHT}布魯斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.15,1:27:00.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,you have the divine spark.\N{\rCHT}你擁有神聖的能力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.07,1:27:05.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You have the gift for bringing joy and laughter to the world.\N{\rCHT}你擁有為世界帶來歡樂的天賦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.16,1:27:08.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I know. I created you.\N{\rCHT}放心! 我知道的 是我創造了你嘛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.66,1:27:12.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Quit bragging. - See?\N{\rCHT}- 你也可以破壞掉它 - 看見了嘛?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.12,1:27:14.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's what I'm talking about.\N{\rCHT}這就是我對你說的你的能力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.50,1:27:16.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's the spark.\N{\rCHT}是一種迸發出的火花!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.42,1:27:23.64,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What do you want me to do?\N{\rCHT}你需要我怎麼做呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.64,1:27:26.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I want you to pray, son.\N{\rCHT}孩子! 我要你學會祈禱!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.06,1:27:30.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Go ahead. Use them.\N{\rCHT}繼續下去 記得用到它們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.11,1:27:39.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Lord, feed the hungry.\N{\rCHT}上帝啊! 請你拯救饑荒中的人們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.36,1:27:42.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And bring peace to...\N{\rCHT}還要為全人類{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.28,1:27:46.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,all of mankind.\N{\rCHT}帶來和平{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.41,1:27:50.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- How's that? - Great.\N{\rCHT}- 我說得怎麼樣? - 太好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.79,1:27:53.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If you want to be Miss America.\N{\rCHT}這是美國小姐的競選詞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.67,1:27:55.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Now, come on.\N{\rCHT}好了! 說吧 你真正關心的東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.79,1:27:57.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What do you really care about?\N{\rCHT}到底什麼才是你真正喜歡的?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.76,1:28:04.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Grace.\N{\rCHT}格雷斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.01,1:28:09.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You want her back?\N{\rCHT}你想回到她身邊?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.52,1:28:15.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No.\N{\rCHT}不{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.73,1:28:18.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I want her to be happy.\N{\rCHT}我只想她能過得開心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.15,1:28:23.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No matter what that means.\N{\rCHT}不管這意味著什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.70,1:28:25.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I want her to find someone\N{\rCHT}我希望她會找到一個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.03,1:28:28.16,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,who'll treat her\N{\rCHT}全身心去愛她的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.08,1:28:33.87,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,with all the love she deserved from me.\N{\rCHT}那是我所欠她的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.50,1:28:38.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I want her to meet someone\N{\rCHT}我想讓她遇上這樣一個人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.88,1:28:45.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,who'll see her always\N{\rCHT}會一直通過她的眼睛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.14,1:28:49.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,as I do now.\N{\rCHT}注視著她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.85,1:28:56.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Through your eyes.\N{\rCHT}像現在的我看你一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.69,1:28:59.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Now that's a prayer. - Yeah?\N{\rCHT}- 這就是你的願望嘛? - 是嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.57,1:29:04.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah. It's good.\N{\rCHT}是的 不錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.24,1:29:11.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm going to get right on it.\N{\rCHT}我會幫你辦妥的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.29,1:29:14.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Clear!\N{\rCHT}好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.33,1:29:16.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That didn't feel very good.\N{\rCHT}這個感覺不是很好!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.75,1:29:20.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Got a rhythm. - I got a pulse.\N{\rCHT}- 檢查他的脈搏 - 有心跳了!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.71,1:29:23.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Let's get him up. - Get the backboard and brace.\N{\rCHT}- 讓我們把他抬上擋架 - 固定好靠背和支柱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.39,1:29:36.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Welcome back.\N{\rCHT}布魯斯 歡迎回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.56,1:29:38.77,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You're lucky to be alive, son.\N{\rCHT}孩子! 你能活著真是很幸運{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.85,1:29:40.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Someone up there must like you.\N{\rCHT}上天一定很眷顧你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.25,1:30:00.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I hear all that stuff winds up in a warehouse somewhere.\N{\rCHT}你還以為這些血被倒掉嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.34,1:30:08.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hi, baby.\N{\rCHT}寶貝 你還好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.26,1:30:13.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, my God, look at you.\N{\rCHT}上帝真是保佑了你啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.39,1:30:17.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I was such an idiot. - It's OK.\N{\rCHT}- 我真是個笨蛋 - 沒關係! 沒關係的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.82,1:30:27.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't know what I would have done.\N{\rCHT}我不知道我應該做些什麼事情{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.53,1:30:33.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, God. I swear I wanted to be mad at you forever.\N{\rCHT}我發誓我想和你永遠在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.04,1:30:47.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Now you're just showing off.\N{\rCHT}我知道是你顯靈了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.64,1:31:00.14,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is Bruce Nolan\N{\rCHT}各位我是 布魯斯·諾蘭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.18,1:31:02.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,here at Buffalo's first "Be the Miracle" blood drive.\N{\rCHT}這裡是水牛鎮的第一屆"創造奇跡"獻血動員會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.77,1:31:05.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's a B - E - A - utiful day.\N{\rCHT}今天是美麗的一天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.77,1:31:09.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,So come on down, because the life you save could be mine.\N{\rCHT}所以請來捐血吧 因為可能這次你拯救的就是我呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.61,1:31:12.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's go over here. The Kowolskis\N{\rCHT}過來看看 我們的科洛斯基為了今天的這個場合{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.85,1:31:14.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,have baked a cookie just for this occasion.\N{\rCHT}他們做了一個十分特殊的餅乾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.66,1:31:17.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sure it's a creepy and a shameless plug, but we love 'em.\N{\rCHT}看上去可能有點嚇人 還帶有一些血{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.87,1:31:20.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you, Mama. VOL - finger, nose.\N{\rCHT}多謝大媽你了 沃爾 注意你的手指{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.12,1:31:24.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I will have given blood twice this week.\N{\rCHT}我本人本周接受了2次捐血{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.54,1:31:26.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,For those of you who haven't heard,\N{\rCHT}為了你們中許多還不知情的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.92,1:31:30.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'd like to introduce you to the future Mrs Exclusive.\N{\rCHT}讓我為你們介紹將來的"布魯斯夫人"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.63,1:31:33.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Grace Connelly. There she is.\N{\rCHT}格雷斯·康納利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.89,1:31:37.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Look at her! Isn't she beautiful?\N{\rCHT}大家看看她吧 她漂亮嘛?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.51,1:31:42.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,She just gave blood and she still has enough left to fill up her face.\N{\rCHT}她剛剛捐了血 但我看她臉上還有足夠的血色{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.69,1:31:46.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes, behind every great man, there's a woman rolling her eyes, folks.\N{\rCHT}每個成功男人的背後 都有一個溫柔的女人在支持著他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.69,1:31:51.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm Bruce Nolan for Eyewitness News reminding you to...\N{\rCHT}我是"新聞直擊"的布魯斯·諾蘭 和我一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.36,1:31:54.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Be the miracle!\N{\rCHT}創造奇跡!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.24,1:31:56.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You heard 'em.\N{\rCHT}聽到了嘛?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.82,1:32:00.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- OK, cut it. Thank you, Bruce. - Thanks, Ally.\N{\rCHT}- 好了! 停 多謝了布魯斯 - 多謝 埃莉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.46,1:32:06.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- How was that? - Great. That was really great.\N{\rCHT}- 感覺怎麼樣? - 真是棒極了! 感覺真是很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.00,1:32:09.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Now go over there. The nurse is waiting.\N{\rCHT}好了 現在在你的後面 護士們在等著你呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.50,1:32:11.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Do I have to? - Oh, it's not going to hurt.\N{\rCHT}- 會痛嘛? - 不會的啦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.88,1:32:14.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,In fact, I think you'll find it pleasurable.\N{\rCHT}實際上 你會發現這很有快感呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.76,1:32:16.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Baby.\N{\rCHT}寶貝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.69,1:33:18.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Who can take a rainbow, wrap it in a sock\N{\rCHT}誰能製造一個彩虹 想一口氣就搞定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.91,1:33:24.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Soak it in the sun and make a groovy lemon pie?\N{\rCHT}在太陽裡面浸一下 然後做一個檸檬餡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.25,1:33:32.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, Jesus.\N{\rCHT}噠 噢 天哪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.67,1:33:34.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm sorry.\N{\rCHT}對不起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.92,1:33:38.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm a very rare blood type. I'm AB positive.\N{\rCHT}我的血型非常特殊 我是AB+{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.89,1:33:41.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sounds delicious.\N{\rCHT}聽起來味道一定很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.81,1:33:47.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, there are storehouses all over the world\N{\rCHT}是的 世界上到處都有倉庫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.77,1:33:51.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,with tons of stuff on ice, and...\N{\rCHT}你知道的 所有... 冰上面有非常多的東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.19,1:33:54.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Sorry. - You were like this. Sorry, go on.\N{\rCHT}- 這是... 對不起 - 你就像這個 對不起 繼續{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.78,1:33:59.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Positive, IB positive... Sorry.\N{\rCHT}陽性 IB+ 對不起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.16,1:34:01.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I have a rary...\N{\rCHT}我有一個"寶貝"...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.87,1:34:04.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,She has a rary!\N{\rCHT}她有一個"寶貝"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.04,1:34:07.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I have a very rare blood type.\N{\rCHT}他們需要我的血 我的是稀有血種{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.58,1:34:09.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm AB negative.\N{\rCHT}我是AB -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.29,1:34:11.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I'm IB positive. - Am I AB negative?\N{\rCHT}- 我是IB+ - 我是AB- {\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.46,1:34:13.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't know what you are any more.\N{\rCHT}我都不知道你是什麼的了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.05,1:34:17.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm going to need a frickin' miracle to get to work on time.\N{\rCHT}我現在需要一個奇跡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.61,1:34:42.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That'll work.\N{\rCHT}應該可以{\r}
